wever%2C%20the%20ability%20for%20anyone%20%E2%80%93%20amateurs%20and%20professionals%20alike%20%E2%80%93%20to%20create%20a%20screenplay%20and%20conjure%20the%20likeness%20of%20an%20existing%20actor%20means%20that%20the%20skills%20once%20specific%20to%20writers%20and%20the%20likeness%20that%20an%20actor%20once%20could%20uniquely%20call%20his%20or%20her%20own%20are%20now%20readily%20available%20%E2%80%93%20with%20questionable%20quality%2C%20to%20be%20sure%20%E2%80%93%20to%20anyone%20with%20access%20to%20these%20free%20online%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20rate%20of%20technological%20change%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20all%20this%20material%20created%20through%20generative%20AI%20is%20destined%20to%20improve%20visually%2C%20not%20only%20for%20people%20like%20me%20and%20social%20media%20creatives%20globally%2C%20but%20possibly%20for%20the%20studios%2C%20which%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20access%20to%20much%20more%20powerful%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20these%20separate%20steps%20%E2%80%93%20preproduction%2C%20screenwriting%2C%20production%2C%20postproduction%20%E2%80%93%20could%20be%20absorbed%20into%20a%20streamlined%20prompting%20system%20that%20bears%20little%20resemblance%20to%20today%E2%80%99s%20art%20and%20craft%20of%20moviemaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FeK9QWB1OOro%3Fwmode%3Dtransparent%26start%3D0%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22260%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriters%20fear%20that%2C%20at%20best%2C%20they%20will%20be%20hired%20to%20edit%20screenplays%20drafted%20by%20AI.%20They%20fear%20that%20their%20creative%20work%20will%20be%20swallowed%20whole%20into%20databases%20as%20the%20fodder%20for%20writing%20tools%20to%20sample.%20And%20they%20fear%20that%20their%20specific%20expertise%20will%20be%20pushed%20aside%20in%20favor%20of%20%E2%80%9Cprompt%20engineers%E2%80%9D%2C%20or%20those%20skilled%20at%20working%20with%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20actors%20fret%20that%20they%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20sell%20their%20likeness%20once%2C%20only%20to%20see%20it%20used%20over%20and%20over%20by%20studios.%20They%20fear%20that%20deepfake%20technologies%20will%20become%20the%20norm%2C%20and%20real%2C%20live%20actors%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20needed%20at%20all.%20And%20they%20worry%20that%20not%20only%20their%20bodies%20but%20their%20voices%20will%20be%20taken%2C%20synthesised%20and%20reused%20without%20continued%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20all%20of%20this%20is%20on%20top%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fculture%2Fnotes-on-hollywood%2Forange-is-the-new-black-signalled-the-rot-inside-the-streaming-economy%5C%22%3Edwindling%20incomes%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20road%20to%20the%20AI%20future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20their%20fears%20justified%3F%20Sort%20of.%20In%20June%202023%2C%20Marvel%20showcased%20titles%20%E2%80%93%20opening%20sequences%20with%20episode%20names%20%E2%80%93%20for%20the%20series%20%E2%80%9CSecret%20Invasion%E2%80%9D%20on%20Disney%2B%20that%20were%20created%20in%20part%20with%20AI%20tools.%20The%20use%20of%20AI%20by%20a%20major%20studio%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgizmodo.com%2Fsecret-invasion-ai-art-opening-credits-marvel-vfx-1850560454%5C%22%3Esparked%20controversy%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20in%20part%20to%20the%20timing%20and%20fears%20about%20AI%20displacing%20people%20from%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20series%20director%20and%20executive%20producer%20Ali%20Selim%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polygon.com%2F23767640%2Fai-mcu-secret-invasion-opening-credits%5C%22%3Etone-deaf%20description%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20only%20added%20to%20the%20sense%20that%20there%20is%20little%20concern%20at%20all%20about%20those%20fears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20on%20July%2026%2C%20software%20developer%20Nicholas%20Neubert%20posted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiamneubert%2Fstatus%2F1684262309340774407%5C%22%3Ea%2048-second%20trailer%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20sci-fi%20film%20made%20with%20images%20made%20by%20AI%20image%20generator%20Midjourney%20and%20motion%20created%20by%20Runway%E2%80%99s%20image-to-motion%20generator%2C%20Gen-2.%20It%20looks%20terrific.%20No%20screenwriter%20was%20hired.%20No%20actors%20were%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20a%20company%20called%20Fable%20released%20Showrunner%20AI%2C%20which%20is%20designed%20to%20allow%20users%20to%20submit%20images%20and%20voices%2C%20along%20with%20a%20brief%20prompt.%20The%20tool%20responds%20by%20creating%20entire%20episodes%20that%20include%20the%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20creators%20have%20been%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2023%2Fjul%2F20%2Fai-tool-creates-south-park-episodes-with-user-in-starring-role%5C%22%3ESouth%20Park%20as%20their%20sample%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20they%20have%20presented%20plausible%20new%20episodes%20of%20the%20show%20that%20integrate%20viewers%20as%20characters%20in%20the%20story.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20create%20a%20new%20form%20of%20audience%20engagement.%20However%2C%20for%20both%20writers%20and%20actors%2C%20Showrunner%20AI%20must%20be%20chilling%20indeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fartificial-intelligence-india-experiment%5C%22%3EWhat%20India%20Should%20Remember%20When%20it%20Comes%20to%20Experimenting%20With%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Volkswagen%20recently%20produced%20a%20commercial%20that%20features%20an%20AI%20reincarnation%20of%20Brazilian%20musician%20Elis%20Regina%2C%20who%20died%20in%201982.%20Directed%20by%20Dulcidio%20Caldeira%2C%20it%20shows%20the%20musician%20as%20she%20appears%20to%20sing%20a%20duet%20with%20her%20daughter.%20For%20some%2C%20the%20song%20was%20a%20beautiful%20revelation%2C%20crafting%20a%20poignant%20mother-daughter%20reunion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20for%20others%2C%20the%20AI%20regeneration%20of%20someone%20who%20has%20died%20prompts%20worries%20about%20how%20one%E2%80%99s%20likeness%20might%20be%20used%20after%20death.%20What%20if%20you%20are%20morally%20opposed%20to%20a%20particular%20film%20project%2C%20TV%20show%20or%20commercial%3F%20How%20will%20actors%20%E2%80%93%20and%20others%20%E2%80%93%20be%20able%20to%20retain%20control%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeeping%20actors%20and%20writers%20in%20the%20credits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriters%E2%80%99%20and%20actors%E2%80%99%20fears%20could%20be%20assuaged%20if%20the%20entertainment%20industry%20developed%20a%20convincing%20and%20inclusive%20vision%20that%20acknowledges%20advances%20in%20AI%2C%20but%20that%20collaborates%20with%20writers%20and%20actors%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20cinematographers%2C%20directors%2C%20art%20designers%20and%20others%2C%20as%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20moment%2C%20developers%20are%20rapidly%20building%20and%20improving%20AI%20tools.%20Production%20companies%20are%20likely%20to%20use%20them%20to%20dramatically%20cut%20costs%2C%20which%20will%20contribute%20to%20a%20massive%20shift%20toward%20a%20gig-oriented%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20dismissive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fentertainment-arts%2Fbusiness%2Fstory%2F2023-07-18%2Fsag-aftra-strike-bob-iger-fran-drescher-barry-diller-david-zaslav-revolution%5C%22%3Eattitude%20toward%20writers%20and%20actors%3C%2Fa%3E%20held%20by%20many%20of%20the%20major%20studios%20continues%2C%20not%20only%20will%20there%20be%20little%20consideration%20of%20the%20needs%20of%20writers%20and%20actors%2C%20but%20technology%20development%20will%20lead%20the%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20if%20the%20tools%20were%20designed%20with%20the%20participation%20of