A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boy%2C%207%2C%20Attacked%20By%20Stray%20Dogs%20In%20UP's%20Jhansi%2C%20Neighbours%20Come%20To%20Rescue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20seven-year-old%20boy%20suffered%20serious%20injuries%20in%20an%20attack%20by%20stray%20dogs%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Jhansi%20last%20evening.%20The%20child%2C%20who%20had%20stepped%20out%20to%20buy%20chocolates%2C%20was%20saved%20by%20his%20neighbours%20who%20heard%20him%20screaming%20and%20scared%20the%20animals%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20footage%20from%20the%20area%20captured%20the%20traumatic%20incident%20in%20which%20seven-year-old%20Virat%20was%20attacked%20by%20five%20dogs%20as%20he%20was%20walking%20to%20a%20shop%20near%20his%20home.%20As%20he%20boy%20screamed%2C%20neighbours%20rushed%20out%20and%20found%20him%20struggling%20to%20keep%20the%20dogs%20off.%20They%20then%20used%20lathis%20to%20scare%20away%20the%20canines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visuals%20show%20the%20pack%20of%20dogs%20pounce%20on%20the%20boy%20as%20he%20tries%20to%20escape.%20They%20pull%20him%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20are%20seen%20biting%20him.%20The%20boy%20has%20suffered%20several%20injuries%20and%20was%20shaken%20by%20the%20horrifying%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat's%20mother%20Lakshmi%20Gupta%20has%20said%20she%20was%20busy%20with%20household%20chores%20when%20she%20heard%20the%20dogs%20bark%20together.%20%26quot%3BI%20feared%20they%20had%20attacked%20someone.%20When%20I%20rushed%20out%2C%20I%20found%20them%20biting%20and%20scratching%20my%20son.%20My%20neighbour%20saved%20him%20and%20brought%20him%20home.%20He%20is%20traumatised%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gupta%20accused%20the%20civic%20authorities%20of%20inaction.%20%26quot%3BThey%20come%20with%20dog%20catching%20squads%20but%20there%20is%20not%20action.%20Even%20other%20neighbourhoods%20of%20Jhansi%20are%20facing%20the%20terror%20of%20stray%20dogs%2C%20but%20the%20officials%20are%20indifferent%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3