20throat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20titled%20%26quot%3BSnap%2C%20crackle%2C%20and%20pop%3A%20when%20sneezing%20leads%20to%20crackling%20in%20the%20neck%26quot%3B%20claimed%20that%20the%20man%20%26quot%3Btried%20to%20halt%20a%20sneeze%20by%20pinching%20the%20nose%20and%20holding%20his%20mouth%20closed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20to%20have%20strange%20symptoms%20including%20painful%20swallowing%2C%20a%20change%20in%20his%20voice%2C%20and%20a%20popping%20sensation%20and%20swelling%20in%20his%20neck.%20He%20decided%20to%20seek%20medical%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20said%20that%20streaks%20of%20air%20had%20become%20trapped%20in%20some%20of%20his%20throat%20tissue%20and%20ruptured%20his%20throat.%20Spontaneous%20rupture%20of%20the%20pharynx%20is%20very%20rare%2C%20usually%20caused%20by%20vomiting%2C%20retching%2C%20heavy%20coughing%20or%20some%20kind%20of%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EBe%20careful%20when%20sneezing%20while%20holding%20your%20nose%20and%20closing%20your%20mouth%2C%20read%20'Snap%2C%20crackle%20and%20pop%3A%20when%20sneezing%20leads%20to%20crackling%20in%20the%20neck'%20here%20%3E%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fj5NLNyxArZ%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fj5NLNyxArZ%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FsLrqhMlDyB%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FsLrqhMlDyB%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20BMJCaseReports%20(%40BMJCaseReports)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBMJCaseReports%2Fstatus%2F953292788333981698%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2016%2C%202018%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20was%20taken%20under%20medical%20observation%20to%20further%20avoid%20the%20risk%20or%20progression%20of%20any%20deep%20neck%20infection.%20The%20patient%20was%20given%20a%20feeding%20tube%20and%20antibiotics.%20He%20recovered%20after%20two%20weeks%20and%20started%20eating%20soft%20foods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHalting%20sneeze%20via%20blocking%20nostrils%20and%20mouth%20is%20a%20dangerous%20manoeuvre%20and%20should%20be%20avoided%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20lead%20to%20numerous%20complications%2C%20such%20as%20pseudomediastinum%20%5Bair%20trapped%20in%20the%20chest%20between%20both%20lungs%5D%2C%20perforation%20of%20the%20tympanic%20membrane%20%5Bperforated%20eardrum%5D%2C%20and%20even%20rupture%20of%20a%20cerebral%20aneurysm%20%5Bballooning%20blood%20vessel%20in%20the%20brain%5D.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692002520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F4q4sqtog_man-who-ruptured-his-throat_625x300_14_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fwhen-a-british-man-blew-a-hole-in-his-throat-after-holding-in-a-sneeze-4296329%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20started%20to%20have%20strange%20symptoms%20including%20painful%20swallowing%2C%20a%20change%20in%20his%20voice%2C%20and%20a%20popping%20sensation%20and%20swelling%20in%20his%20neck.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fwhen-a-british-man-blew-a-hole-in-his-throat-after-holding-in-a-sneeze-4296329%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fwhen-a-british-man-blew-a-hole-in-his-throat-after-holding-in-a-sneeze-4296329%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fwhen-a-british-man-blew-a-hole-in-his-throat-after-holding-in-a-sneeze-4296329%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Team%20India%20Creates%20'Unwanted%20Records'%20With%20Shock%20T20I%20Series%20Defeat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUp%20against%20West%20Indies%20in%20tour%20that%20consisted%20of%202%20Tests%2C%203%20ODIs%20and%205%20T20Is%2C%20the%20expectations%20from%20the%20subcont