Violence%20In%20Manipur%20Explained%20By%20Army%20Veteran%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERestive%20Manipur%20has%20seen%20unprecedented%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20Kuki-Chin-Zo%20tribes%20for%20over%20three%20months%20with%20no%20sign%20of%20respite.%20Notwithstanding%20the%20government%20and%20civil%20bodies'%20call%20for%20peace%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20violence%20has%20gone%20down%20only%20a%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20string%20of%20clashes%20that%20unfolded%20in%20the%20northeast%20state%20since%20May%203%20has%20killed%20more%20than%20180%20people%2C%20wounded%20over%20200%20and%20reduced%20hundreds%20of%20villages%20and%20numerous%20government%20and%20private%20properties%20into%20ashes%2C%20besides%20forcing%20over%2050%2C000%20people%20to%20take%20refuge%20in%20relief%20camps%20spread%20over%20the%20valley%20and%20hill%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHorrific%20murders%20-%20during%20sleep%2C%20execution-style%20and%20beheading%2C%20and%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20including%20parading%20them%20naked%2C%20were%20the%20worst-ever%20incidents%20during%20the%20violence%2C%20prompting%20%C2%A0the%20whole%20nation%20and%20the%20world%20to%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20shocking%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20big%20threat%20to%20security%20was%20the%20looting%20of%204%2C000%20arms%2C%20ammunition%20and%20bombs%20by%20mobs%20from%20police%20armouries%20since%20the%20violence%20broke%20out%2C%20first%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20in%20the%20valley.%20The%20police%20have%20recovered%20some%20of%20these%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20spoke%20to%20Lieutenant%20General%20Laiphrakpam%20Nishikanta%20Singh%20(retired)%2C%20who%20has%20been%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20Manipur%20situation.%20Lt%20Gen%20Singh%20is%20the%20third%20person%20from%20the%20northeast%20to%20have%20attained%20the%20second-highest%20rank%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20The%20rescue%20mission%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20after%20the%20Indian%20medical%20mission%20there%20was%20attacked%20in%20February%202010%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20missions%20he%20led%20during%20his%20career.%20He%20also%20headed%20the%20Intelligence%20Corps%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20before%20retiring%20in%202018%2C%20after%2040%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22tt5eq544%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Ftt5eq544_manipur-violence-1200_625x300_17_June_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcerpts%20from%20the%20interview%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ%3A%20As%20a%20security%20intelligence%20veteran%2C%20how%20do%20you%20see%20the%20looting%20of%20weapons%20and%20ammunition%20from%20the%20police%20armouries%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELt%20General%20Singh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20first%20looting%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20started%20in%20Churachandpur%20when%20miscreants%20looted%20a%20gun%20shop%20and%20the%20police%20station%20and%20snatched%20weapons%20from%20security%20personnel%20there.%20As%20a%20reaction%20to%20it%2C%20there%20were%20lootings%20in%20the%20valley%20too.%20But%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20analysed%20here%20is%20that%20the%20Kukis%20have%20been%20fighting%20for%20over%2090%20days%20now.%20The%20Assam%20Rifles%20said%20that%20the%20cadre%20of%20the%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20group%20along%20with%20their%20arms%20are%20in%20the%20camps.%20If%20that%20is%20the%20case%2C%20how%20are%20the%20Kuki%20insurgents%20firing%20at%20Meitei%20villages%20almost%20every%20day%3F%20How%20are%20they%20sustaining%20themselves%3F%20Keep%20in%20mind%20they%20are%20using%20sophisticated%20weapons%20like%20sniper%20rifles%2C%20grenade%20launchers%2C%20two-inch%20mortars.%20So%2C%20again%2C%20the%20question%20is%20how%20are%20they%20sustaining%20themselves%20for%20such%20a%20long%20time%3F%20It%20has%20been%20more%20than%2090%20days.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20significant%20aspects%20of%20the%20Manipur%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComparatively%2C%20the%20other%20side%20does%20not%20really%20have%20any%20weapons%2C%20so%20to%20say.%20By%20no%20means%20I'm%20condoning%20the%20looting%20of%20the%20police%20armouries%20in%20the%20valley.%20But%20I%20feel%20the%20public%20was%20compelled%20by%20the%20situation.%20With%20the%20Kuki%20insurgents%20firing%20on%20them%20every%20single%20day%2C%20I%20guess%20the%20public%20ran%20berserk%20and%20decided%20to%20arm%20themselves%20by%20hook%20or%20crook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20my%20perspective%2C%20the%20fighting%20may%20be%20clubbed%20into%20phases.%20Phase%201%20was%20from%20May%203%20to%20May%2010-11%2C%20characterised%20by%20low-intensity%20gunfights.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20intensity%20was%20more%20and%20sometimes%2C%20much%20less.%20Phase%202%20was%20when%20coordinated%20attacks%20started%20on%20Imphal%20valley%20from%20all%20directions%20on%20May%2027%20and%2028.%20This%20phase%20was%20distinct%20by%20the%20high-intensity%20fighting%20that%20went%20on%20for%20many%20days.%20Unless%20there%20is%20a%20move%20to%20disarm%20both%20sides%2C%20the%20fighting%20is%20likely%20to%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ%3A%20Were%20the%20police%20not%20prepared%20to%20stop%20the%20looting%20of%20their%20armouries%3F%20How%20exactly%20did%20the%20looting%20take%20place%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELt%20General%20Singh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Looting%20of%20arms%20from%20police%20stations%20is%20not%20something%20that%20has%20happened%20only%20in%20Manipur.%20It%20has%20occurred%20in%20many%20places.%20A%20long%20time%20ago%2C%20when%20I%20was%20a%20young%20Major%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20the%20Purulia%20police%20arrested%20two%20terrorists.%20They%20were%20unarmed.%20But%20they%20looted%20weapons%20from%20the%20police%20station%20and%20shot%20dead%2011%20policemen.%20Looting%20of%20weapons%20does%20happen%2C%20especially%20when%20there%20is%20desperation.%20And%20when%20you%20say%20police%20station%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20hundred%20people%20guarding%20a%20police%20station.%20A%20police%20station%20at%20best%20has%20got%2025-30%20people%2C%20of%20which%205-10%20are%20out%20on%20duty.%20So%20the%20strength%20of%20a%20police%20station%20at%20any%20given%20time%20may%20be%2010-15%20people%20only.%20Imagine%2C%20a%20mob%20of%202%2C000-3%2C000%20coming%20to%20a%20police%20station%3B%20it%20would%20be%20very%20difficult%20even%20for%20the%20two-three%20sentries%20to%20open%20fire%20on%20the%20crowd%20because%20such%20a%20situation%20has%20got%20its%20own%20legal%2C%20psychological%20and%20other%20implications.%20That%20is%20how%20the%20weapons%20were%20looted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22agv4goho%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fagv4goho_manipur-violence-ani_625x300_12_June_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ%3A%20Many%20have%20criticised%20what%20they%20called%20the%20inefficiency%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20in%20tackling%20the%20situation.%20In%20fact%2C%20many%20are%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20because%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Police's%20poor%20handling%20of%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%2C%20the%20violence%20spiralled%20out%20of%20control.%20Where%20do%20you%20think%20lies%20the%20fault%20with%20the%20police%20in%20law%20and%20order%20issues%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELt%20General%20Singh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20What%20started%20on%20May%203%20was%20not%20a%20simple%20law%20and%20order%20situation.%20It%20was%20a%20massive%20communal%20riot.%20If%20you%20remember%20the%20communal%20riots%20in%20Delhi%20in%201984%20and%20other%20places%2C%20initially%20the%20police%20were%20not%20able%20to%20tackle%20them.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Manipur%2C%20the%20police%20had%20to%20encounter%20two%20groups%20of%20people.%20One%20group%20was%20sophisticatedly%20armed%20with%20a%20good%20supply%20of%20ammunition.%20They%20had%20weapons%20that%20could%20take%20on%20the%20police%20and%20the%20other%20group%20had%20the%20crowds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20were%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20violence.%20From%20May%204%20the%20central%20government%20sent%20numerous%20paramilitary%20forces%20by%20air.%20According%20to%20a%20rough%20estimate%2C%20the%20total%20number%20of%20security%20forces%20stationed%20in%20the%20state%20today%20is%2060%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20are%20to%20blame%20the%20police%20for%20inefficiency%2C%20we%20must%20take%20into%20consideration%20the%2060%2C000%20central%20security%20personnel%2C%20who%20have%20been%20in%20the%20state%20for%20over%20three%20months%2C%20also%20found%20it%20extremely%20challenging%20to%20control%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20agree%20if%20the%20violence%20was%20contained%20in%20the%20initial%20phase%2C%20the%20situation%20would%20have%20been%20controlled.%20But%20the%20question%20is%2C%20in%20the%20past%2090%20days%2C%20have%20we%20really%20made%20progress%20on%20containing%20the%20situation%3F%20I%20really%20do%20not%20know.%20Firing%20happens%20every%20day.%20There%20is%20not%20a%20day%20without%20a%20Meitei%20village%20being%20fired%20upon%20by%20insurgents%20from%20the%20foothills.%20Unfortunately%2C%20if%20such%20a%20massive%20central%20force%20including%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20BSF%20and%20CRPF%20couldn't%20contain%20the%20violence%20fully%2C%20expecting%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20to%20contain%20it%20on%20their%20own%20is%20something%20that%20may%20not%20be%20fair%20to%20the%20state%20forces.%20I%20believe%20that%20soon%20the%20security%20forces%20will%20be%20able%20to%20contain%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ%3A%20The%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20Manipur%20Police%20commandos%20are%20key%20forces%20operating%20in%20the%20state%20for%20decades.%20This%20time%2C%20there%20were%20allegations%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20and%20issues%20of%20distrust.%20How%20far%20is%20that%20harming%20the%20security%20scenario%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELt%20General%20Singh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Trust%20deficit%20does%20exist.%20Remember%2C%20when%20the%20trouble%20began%2C%20the%20Kukis%20made%20a%20presentation%20to%20the%20Defence%20Ministry%20for%20posting%20out%2023%20Meitei%20officers%20who%20are%20posted%20here.%20That%20is%20the%20level%20of%20trust%20deficit.%20It%20is%20not%20only%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20that%20they%20don't%20trust.%20They%20even%20distrust%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20the%20Indian%20Army%20wherever%20there%20is%20a%20Meitei%20officer%2C%20as%20they%20perceive%20it%20would%20be%20harming%20their%20cause.%20This%20is%20one%20aspect.%20You%20would%20be%20surprised%20to%20know%20that%20the%20same%20list%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20UN%20also.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20the%20submission%20the%20Kukis%20have%20made%20to%20the%20UN%2C%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20appendices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20be%20the%20public%20allegations%2C%20the%20authorities%20concerned%20i.e.%20the%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20the%20Manipur%20government%20must%20try%20to%20investigate%20and%20assure%20the%20public%20to%20gain%20their%20confidence.%20If%20what%20is%20being%20alleged%20isn't%20correct%2C%20they%20must%20come%20out%20with%20the%20facts%20of%20the%20cases%20and%20make%20clarifications.%20If%20the%20allegation%20is%20found%20to%20be%20true%2C%20then%20the%20authorities%20must%20rectify%20it%20and%20fix%20responsibilities.%20The%20defaulters%20can%20be%20either%20sidestepped%20or%20some%20sort%20of%20penalty%20imposed%20so%20that%20the%20act%20is%20not%20repeated.%20These%20measures%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20addressing%20the%20trust%20deficit%20in%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20today%2C%20the%20Meiteis%20don't%20trust%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20the%20Kukis%20don't%20trust%20the%20state%20forces.%20Remember%2C%20Meiteis%20started%20distrusting%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20sometime%20during%20the%20third%20week%2C%20not%20initially%2C%20after%20trouble%20erupted.%20Precisely%20after%20the%20Kukis%20launched%20the%20Phase%202%20of%20the%20attacks.%20Before%20that%20there%20was%20no%20mistrust.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Meiteis%20were%20grateful%20to%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20for%20rescuing%20nearly%2040%2C000%20people%20caught%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20the%20area%20when%20trouble%20started.%20Credit%20must%20be%20given%20to%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20for%20doing%20such%20humanitarian%20work.%20But%20the%20trust%20deficit%20developed%20when%20the%20coordinated%20attacks%20were%20launched%20by%20the%20Kukis%20on%20Imphal%20valley%20on%20the%20night%20of%20May%2027-28.%20Since%20then%2C%20this%20trust%20deficit%20exists%20even%20now.%20I'm%20sure%20the%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20the%20Manipur%20government%20will%20take%20adequate%20actions%20to%20mitigate%20this%20trust%20deficit%20by%20having%20their%20own%20internal%20mechanism%20to%20look%20into%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%225rfn5rvg%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F5rfn5rvg_manipur-violence-ani_625x300_05_June_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ%3A%20Despite%20the%20presence%20of%20central%20forces%20and%20the%20army%2C%20violence%20happened.%20What%20are%20the%20reasons%20of%20failure%20to%20contain%20violence%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELt%20General%20Singh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20force%20does%20what%20is%20directed%20on%20them.%20They%20do%20not%20do%20it%20on%20their%20own.%20Unfortunately%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20such%20a%20large%20number%20of%20forces%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20united%20command%20that%20exists%20needs%20a%20major%20revamp.%20When%20you%20say%20united%20command%2C%20all%20the%20forces%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20integrated.%20The%20word%20to%20be%20used%20is%20not%20Manipur%20Rifles%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20CRPF%2C%20BSF%2C%20etc.%20Instead%2C%20a%20single%20term%20that%20could%20be%20just%20'security%20forces'%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20used.%20The%20press%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20requested%20to%20use%20the%20term%20'security%20forces'%20so%20that%20people%20cannot%20distinguish%20between%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Rifles%2C%20Manipur%20Police%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20the%20BSF%20or%20CRFF%2C%20or%20whatever%20there%20may%20be.%20This%20is%20foremost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20current%20case%2C%20the%20united%20command%20that%20is%20supposed%20to%20integrate%20everyone%20has%20not%20done%20it%20effectively.%20To%20use%20an%20analogy%2C%20it%20is%20like%20putting%20five%20eggs%20in%20a%20basket%20and%20that%20is%20supposed%20to%20integrate%20everyone.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20united%20command.%20You%20have%20to%20break%20each%20egg%20and%20stir%20them%20well%20so%20that%20they%20become%20a%20whole.%20This%20has%20not%20really%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Rifles%20going%20to%20Moreh%20for%20deployment%20to%20contain%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20border%20town%20where%20all%20shops%20and%20houses%20belonging%20to%20the%20Meiteis%20were%20burnt%20down.%20The%20Manipur%20Rifles%20have%20been%20held%20up%20in%20Tengnoupal%20with%20Kuki-Chin-Zo%20women%20blocking%20the%20Asian%20highway%20leading%20to%20Moreh.%20No%20other%20force%20is%20present%20in%20the%20additional%20deployment%20meant%20for%20Moreh.%20So%2C%20is%20that%20a%20united%20command%3F%20This%20decision%20of%20redeploying%20Manipur%20Rifles%20in%20Moreh%20should%20have%20been%20taken%20by%20the%20unified%20command%2C%20and%20they%20should%20have%20ensured%20it.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20deployment%20has%20failed.%20It%20is%20not%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20or%20the%20Manipur%20Rifles.%20It%20is%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20united%20command%20because%20the%20command%20and%20control%20lie%20with%20them.%20The%20security%20agencies%20need%20to%20rethink%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20united%20command%20on%20how%20to%20improve%20it.%20How%20far%20the%20security%20agencies%20are%20integrated%20is%20still%20a%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692001200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fv9ipj8d8_lt-general-l-nishikanta-singh_625x300_14_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-2-phases-of-violence-in-manipur-explained-by-army-veteran-lt-general-l-nishikanta-singh-to-ndtv-4296296%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Restive%20Manipur%20has%20seen%20unprecedented%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20Kuki-Chin-Zo%20tribes%20for%20over%20three%20months%20with%20no%20sign%20of%20respite.%20Notwithstanding%20the%20government%20and%20civil%20bodies'%20call%20for%20peace%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20violence%20has%20gone%20down%20only%20a%20bit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-2-phases-of-violence-in-manipur-explained-by-army-veteran-lt-general-l-nishikanta-singh-to-ndtv-4296296%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-2-phases-of-violence-in-manipur-explained-by-army-veteran-lt-general-l-nishikanta-singh-to-ndtv-4296296%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-2-phases-of-violence-in-manipur-explained-by-army-veteran-lt-general-l-nishikanta-singh-to-ndtv-4296296%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Surjewala%20calls%20BJP%20and%20its%20supporters%20'Rakshas'%2C%20BJP%20takes%20him%20on%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692001046000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102718267%2Cimgsize-36718.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frandeep-surjewala-calls-bjp-and-its-supporters-rakshas-bjp-takes-h