0in%20rural%20Australia%20after%20a%20family%20mushroom%20lunch%20ended%20with%20three%20people%20dead%20and%20a%20local%20preacher%20fighting%20for%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20believe%20the%20dish%20was%20tainted%20with%20%26quot%3Bdeath%20cap%26quot%3B%20mushrooms%2C%20which%20grow%20freely%20in%20the%20rolling%20foothills%20surrounding%20Leongatha%20--%20a%20small%20town%20about%20two%20hours'%20drive%20southeast%20of%20Melbourne.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meal%20was%20cooked%20by%20community%20newsletter%20editor%20Erin%20Patterson%2C%20who%20has%20been%20named%20as%20a%20suspect%20because%20she%20appeared%20to%20remain%20in%20good%20health%20despite%20her%20four%20guests%20falling%20violently%20ill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20has%20fuelled%20intense%20speculation%20as%20police%20try%20to%20separate%20clumsy%20cooking%20from%20an%20alleged%20act%20of%20malice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatterson%20stressed%20on%20Monday%20she%20had%20unwittingly%20brought%20the%20mushrooms%20from%20an%20Asian%20grocery%20store%20and%20that%20the%20poisonings%20were%20accidental.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20now%20devastated%20to%20think%20that%20these%20mushrooms%20may%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20illness%20suffered%20by%20my%20loved%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20reportedly%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20Australian%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20want%20to%20repeat%20that%20I%20had%20absolutely%20no%20reason%20to%20hurt%20these%20people%20whom%20I%20loved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatterson%20prepared%20the%20beef%20Wellington%20for%20her%20estranged%20parents-in-law%20Don%20and%20Gail%20Patterson%20on%20the%20afternoon%20of%20Saturday%2C%20July%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20married%20to%20Don%20and%20Gail's%20son%20Simon%20but%20the%20couple%20had%20been%20living%20separately%20for%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20Baptist%20pastor%20Ian%20Wilkinson%20and%20his%20wife%20Heather%20rounded%20out%20the%20guest%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20night%20the%20two%20couples%20started%20experiencing%20food%20poisoning%20symptoms%20and%2C%20with%20their%20health%20rapidly%20deteriorating%2C%20they%20sought%20the%20help%20of%20doctors%20at%20local%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeather%20and%20Gail%20died%20the%20following%20Friday%2C%20Don%20died%20the%20day%20after%20that%2C%20and%2070-year-old%20Ian%20is%20still%20clinging%20to%20life%20in%20a%20critical%20but%20stable%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20hopeful%20and%20continue%20to%20pray%20for%20his%20recovery%2C%26quot%3B%20Ian's%20family%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20deeply%20moved%20by%20the%20outpouring%20of%20kindness%2C%20prayers%2C%20and%20support%20from%20family%2C%20friends%20and%20the%20broader%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'I'm%20devastated'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForensic%20experts%20have%20been%20testing%20a%20food%20dehydrator%20that%20was%20found%20at%20a%20rubbish%20dump%20nearby%20to%20see%20whether%20it%20contains%20traces%20of%20the%20toxic%20death%20cap%20mushrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Australian%20media%2C%20Patterson%20has%20admitted%20dumping%20the%20dehydrator%20--%20saying%20she%20panicked%20and%20was%20worried%20about%20losing%20custody%20of%20her%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20reportedly%20said%20she%20bought%20the%20mushrooms%20from%20a%20local%20grocery%20store%20in%20Melbourne%20and%20that%20she%20too%20had%20fallen%20ill%20after%20eating%20them%20alongside%20her%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatterson%20has%20forcefully%20protested%20her%20innocence%2C%20tearfully%20telling%20reporters%20last%20week%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20do%20anything%2C%20I%20love%20them%20and%20I'm%20devastated%20they%20are%20gone%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20not%20been%20charged%20and%20police%20have%20provided%20no%20e