C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fback-to-the-theatre-pvr-inox-made-over-rs-100-cr-this-blockbuster-weekend-123081400246_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fback-to-the-theatre-pvr-inox-made-over-rs-100-cr-this-blockbuster-weekend-123081400246_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haryana%20Govt%20Starts%20Process%20to%20Ban%20Intra-Gotra%2C%20Intra-Village%20Marriages%20as%20Per%20Khap%20Panchayats'%20Demands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14121527%2FF3T6TBIb0AAY7VK.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Haryana%20government%20has%20initiated%20the%20process%20of%20amending%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201955%3C%2Fem%3E%20(HMA)%20in%20response%20to%20khap%20panchayats%E2%80%99%20demands%20to%20ban%20intra-gotra%20and%20intra-village%20marriages%20as%20well%20as%20the%20registration%20of%20live-in%20relationships%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fharyana%2Fharyana-government-sets-in-motion-demand-of-khaps-for-amendment-in-hindu-marriage-act-534873%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20Home%20Department%2C%20referred%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%2C%20Citizen%20Resources%20Information%20Department%20(CRID)%20for%20further%20action%2C%20acting%20on%20the%20demands%20submitted%20by%20the%20Bharat%20Bhoomi%20Bachao%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%20president%20Ramesh%20Dalal%20and%20Sarvjatia%20Kandela%20Khap%20head%20Dharam%20Pal%20Kandela.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Kandela%20said%20%E2%80%98same-gotra%20and%20same-village%20marriages%20were%20in%20conflict%20with%20the%20social%20norms%20in%20society%E2%80%99%20and%20they%20had%20submitted%20a%20representation%20to%20the%20state%20government%20for%20amendment%20of%20the%20HMA%20in%20line%20with%20the%20khap%20panchayats%E2%80%99%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20intra-gotra%20and%20intra-village%20marriages%20amount%20to%20social%20stigma%2C%20which%20result%20in%20constant%20humiliation%20and%20mental%20torture%20of%20the%20parents%20whose%20boy%2Fgirl%20solemnise%20such%20marital%20ties%20which%20are%20in%20violation%20of%20social%20norms.%20It%20is%20necessary%20to%20bring%20amendments%20in%20the%20HMA%20to%20accommodate%20the%20conditions%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20social%20norms%20for%20maintaining%20the%20social%20fabric%20and%20a%20happy%20family%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kandela%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalal%20had%20also%20submitted%20a%20representation%20to%20the%20state%20government%20last%20month%20with%20the%20demand%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20intra-gotra%20and%20intra-village%20marriages%2C%20those%20between%20people%20from%20bordering%20villages%20should%20also%20be%20declared%20invalid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalal%20said%20he%20was%20assured%20by%20top%20officials%20of%20the%20government%20that%20the%20matter%20had%20been%20assigned%20to%20a%20senior%20official%20who%20was%20likely%20to%20submit%20the%20final%20report%20to%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThereafter%2C%20the%20CM%20will%20take%20the%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20demand.%20In%20principle%2C%20the%20government%20was%20in%20agreement%20with%20me%20on%20the%20proposal%20for%20amendment%20in%20the%20HMA%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20representation%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20Haryana%20government%20on%20July%201%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh-news%2Fkha