%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeather%20experts%20the%20NDTV%20spoke%20to%20said%20that%20many%20areas%20in%20Himachal%20are%20already%20vulnerable%20following%20the%20monsoon%20fury%20and%20even%20moderate%20rainfall%20in%20these%20areas%20can%20trigger%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2021%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Himachal%20over%20the%20past%2048%20hours%20after%20heavy%20rain%20washed%20away%20homes%20and%20triggered%20the%20collapse%20of%20a%20temple%20in%20Shimla.%20The%20temple%20collapse%20has%20claimed%20nine%20lives%20and%20at%20least%2025%20others%20are%20feared%20trapped.%20The%20fresh%20spell%20of%20rain%20has%20triggered%20landslides%2C%20hitting%20road%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20is%20now%20bracing%20for%20more%20showers%20as%20the%20weather%20office%20has%20predicted%20heavy%20rain%20over%20the%20next%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Sukhwinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20has%20appealed%20to%20people%20to%20stay%20indoors%20and%20said%20efforts%20to%20restore%20connectivity%20at%20the%20earliest%20are%20being%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttarakhand%2C%20heavy%20rain%20has%20caused%20loss%20to%20property.%20A%20video%20showing%20floodwaters%20wash%20away%20a%20multi-storeyed%20college%20building%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20capturing%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20calamity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlaknanda%2C%20Mandakini%20and%20Ganga%20rivers%20are%20flowing%20above%20the%20danger%20level%20at%20Rudraprayag%2C%20Shrinagar%20and%20Devprayag%2C%20the%20disaster%20control%20room%20in%20Dehradun%20said.%20The%20Badrinath%20National%20highway%20is%20blocked%20at%20several%20places%20due%20to%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20spell%20of%20torrential%20rain%20comes%20as%20the%20hill%20states%20were%20limping%20back%20to%20normalcy%20following%20the%20monsoon%20fury%20a%20month%20back%20that%20led%20to%20huge%20loss%20of%20life%20and%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A16919