jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EMadhav%20Damle%20runs%20a%20home%20for%20senior%20citizens%20in%20Wai%2C%20a%20town%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia%2Ft-18996071%5C%22%3EIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20western%20state%20of%20Maharashtra.%20Years%20ago%2C%20his%20job%20made%20him%20face%20an%20uncomfortable%20truth%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20the%20residents%20were%20experiencing%20loneliness%20and%20stress%2C%20and%20had%20poor%20relations%20with%20their%20families%20and%20friends.%20At%20least%20one%20of%20the%20seniors%20under%20his%20care%20tried%20to%20commit%20suicide%20by%20consuming%20sleeping%20pills.%20His%20adult%20children%20expressed%20little%20interest%20in%20taking%C2%A0care%20of%20him%2C%20said%20Damle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20ways%20to%20ease%20his%20clients%E2%80%99%20isolation%2C%20Damle%20had%20an%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20he%20tried%20matching%20them%20into%20couples%20with%20a%20perspective%20of%20marriage.%20This%20worked%20especially%20well%20for%20clients%20in%20their%20mid%20to%20late%2060s.%20But%20he%20then%20faced%20an%20unexpected%20obstacle%2C%20as%20some%20of%20the%20clients%E2%80%99%20children%20disliked%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia-elderly-couple-sue-son-over-lack-of-grandchildren%2Fa-61768426%5C%22%3Eelderly%20relatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20marrying%2C%20due%20to%20inheritance%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%2C%20I%20thought%20live-in%20relationships%20might%20be%20a%20good%20solution%20for%20the%20couples.%20We%20conducted%20a%20survey%20among%20some%20seniors%20in%20%5Bthe%20Maharashtra%20city%20of%5D%20Pune%2C%20and%20about%2070%25%20of%20them%20were%20open%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20live-in%20partner%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Time%20and%20love%E2%80%99%20as%20top%20priorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20society%20is%20remarkably%20conservative%20when%20it%C2%A0comes%20to%20marriage%20and%20relationships.%20The%20divorce%20rate%20in%20India%20is%20about%201%25%20%E2%80%94%20among%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20world.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20is%20a%20social%20stigma%20against%20remarrying%20and%20against%20unmarried%20couples%20living%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20even%20made%20it%20to%20the%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202006%2C%20with%20the%20judges%20finding%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Clive-in%20relationship%20between%20two%20consenting%20adults%20of%20heterogenic%20sex%20does%20not%20amount%20to%20any%20offense%2C%20even%20though%20it%20may%20be%20perceived%20as%20immoral.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDamle%20officially%20started%20his%20matchmaking%20agency%20in%202012%2C%20which%20later%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9CHappy%20Seniors.%E2%80%9D%20He%20is%20managing%20and%20sharing%20profiles%2C%20while%20also%20organizing%20meet-ups%20and%20trips%20for%20his%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20Savgave%20and%20Saroj%20Ghatani%20found%20each%20other%20through%20Damle.%20The%20two%20are%20now%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20only%20requirement%20from%20a%20partner%20was%20their%20time%20and%20love.%20I%20got%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ghatani%20told%20DW.%20She%20added%20that%20her%20family%20did%20not%20approve%20of%20her%20new%20marriage%2C%20but%20this%20did%20not%20deter%20her%20and%C2%A0Savgave.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20enjoy%20each%20others%E2%80%99%20company%20and%20spend%20most%20of%20our%20time%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Ghatani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESavgave%E2%80%99s%20family%20was%20more%20supportive.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20vegetarian%2C%20whereas%20I%20eat%20meat%20frequently%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20have%20adapted%20to%20each%20other%20and%20enjoy%20the%20companionship.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinefield%20of%20dating%20apps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findianmatchmakingfraught-with-sexism-class-and-caste-issues%2Fa-55174165%5C%22%3EMatchmaking%20is%20a%20time-honored%20craft%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%20But%20finding%20a%20partner%20online%20is%20growing%20increasingly%20common%2C%20and%20even%20some%20older%20Indians%20are%20turning%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhow-indians-with-disabilities-find-love-through-dating-apps%2Fa-64784892%5C%22%3Emodern%20dating%20apps%20to%20find%20love%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETina%20(name%20changed)%2C%2064%2C%20decided%20to%20do%20just%20that%20after%20walking%20out%20of%20an%20abusive%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20married%20at%2018%20and%20became%20a%20mum%20by%2020%2C%20I%20never%20got%20the%20chance%20to%20be%20myself.%C2%A0%20So%20after%20I%20split%2C%20I%20had%20all%20this%20freedom%20and%20no%20one%20to%20dictate%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20while%2C%20she%20tried%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fonline-dating%2Ft-38790642%5C%22%3Edating%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20search%20of%20companionship.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20a%20lot%20of%20men%20were%20married%2C%20and%20looking%20to%20cheat%20on%20their%20wives.%20There%20were%20also%20some%20younger%20men%20looking%20for%20an%20older%20woman.%20I%20got%20fed%20up%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20admitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20frustration%20eventually%20paid%20off.%20She%20found%20a%20partner%20through%20an%20app%2C%20and%20%E2%80%94%20after%20chatting%20for%20about%20five%20years%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20the%20two%20finally%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20both%20definitely%20not%20looking%20for%20marriage.%20Just%20companionship%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20children%20know%20about%20her%20relationship.%20Her%20partner%20also%20has%20one%20child%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20acceptance%20has%20not%20been%20forthcoming%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tina%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMost%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20seniors%20lonely%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20breaking%20taboos%20is%20likely%20to%20grow%20increasingly%20common%20as%20both%20India%E2%80%99s%20society%20and%20its%20population%20shift.%20Today%2C%20about%205.7%25%20of%20Indian%20senior%20citizens%20live%20alone%20without%20the%20support%20of%20family%20or%20friends%2C%20according%20to%20a%20survey%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20PAN%20Healthcare.%20It%20was%20conducted%20among%2010%2C000%20elderly%20population%20across%2010%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20and%20also%20found%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20responders%20feel%20lonely%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20with%20India%20now%20the%20most%20populous%20country%20in%20the%20word%2C%20the%20number%20of%20its%20seniors%20is%20climbing%20%E2%80%94%20the%20UN%20Population%20Fund%20said%20it%20will%20touch%20192%20million%20by%202030%2C%20and%2C%20by%202050%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fdemographics%2Ft-62940381%5C%22%3Eevery%20fifth%20Indian%20will%20be%20an%20elderly%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20defined%20by%20the%20UN%20as%20aged%2060%20or%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhow-elderly-citizens-in-india-are-finding-love%2Fa-66504452%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691995559000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14085245%2FVillagers_from_india_16.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fhow-elderly-citizens-in-india-are-finding-love%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20and%20more%20Indian%20seniors%20are%20refusing%20to%20spend%20their%20twilight%20years%20alone%20and%20are%20turning%20to%20matchmaking%20and%20dating%20apps.%20But%20this%20means%20breaking%20some%20deep-seated%20taboos.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canoni