s%20also%20been%20trying%20to%20develop%20high-grade%20laser%20systems.%20These%20include%20the%20Navy%20Advanced%20Chemical%20Laser%20(NACL)%2C%20the%20Middle%20Infrared%20Advanced%20Chemical%20Laser%20(MIRACL)%2C%20the%20Tactical%20High%20Energy%20Laser%20(THEL)%20and%20the%20Space-Based%20Laser%20(SBL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military%20tested%20these%20weapons%20in%20the%20field%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20even%20destroyed%20supersonic%20missiles%2C%20they%20were%20cancelled%20owing%20to%20large%20size%20and%20weight%20of%20lasers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20range%20was%20only%20a%20few%20kilometres%2C%20but%20Yuan's%20team%20said%20to%20have%20improved%20the%20destructive%20power%20of%20a%20laser%20beam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20experts%20are%20keeping%20a%20keen%20eye%20on%20developments%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20have%20overcome%20the%20heating%20and%20distortion%20issues%20as%20claimed%2C%20in%20a%20(relatively)%20small%20enough%20unit%20for%20deployment%2C%20this%20is%20a%20big%20breakthrough%20considering%20the%20US%20failures%20in%20this%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20British%20military%20official%20Steve%20Weaver%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EChinese%20scientists%20achieve%20laser%20weapon%20technology%20%E2%80%98breakthrough'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FaA77jCMeg7%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FaA77jCMeg7%3C%2Fa%3E%20via%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSCMPNews%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40scmpnews%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIf%20they%20have%20overcome%20the%20heating%20and%20distortion%20issues%20as%20claimed%2C%20in%20a%20(relatively)%20small%20enough%20unit%20for%20deployment%2C%20this%20is%20a%20big%20breakthrough%20considering%20the%20US%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbjAPebsAWw%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbjAPebsAWw%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Steve%20Weaver%20%F0%9F%87%AC%F0%9F%87%A7%F0%9F%87%A8%F0%9F%87%B3%F0%9F%8F%89%20(%40SteveWeaverTEFL)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSteveWeaverTEFL%2Fstatus%2F1689952097351983104%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20system%20also%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20more%20cost-effective%20than%20traditional%20missile-based%20systems%20as%20it%20does%20not%20require%20expensive%20munitions%20and%20can%20be%20recharged%20quickly.%C2%A0If%20necessary%2C%20China%20also%20plans%20to%20use%20laser%20weapons%20against%20satellites%20such%20as%20SpaceX's%20Starlink%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20a%20laser%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NASA%2C%20laser%20is%20a%20special%20type%20of%20light%20that%20has%20been%20artificially%20created.%20It%20produces%20a%20narrow%20beam%20of%20light%20in%20which%20all%20the%20light%20waves%20have%20very%20similar%20wavelengths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20laser's%20light%20waves%20travel%20together%20with%20their%20peaks%20all%20lined%20up%2C%20of%20in%20phase.%20This%20unique%20property%20makes%20laser%20beams%20very%20narrow%2C%20very%20bright%20and%20focussed%20into%20a%20very%20tight%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20can%20travel%20very%20long%20distances%20and%20concentrate%20a%20lot%20of%20energy%20on%20a%20very%20small%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20beam%20is%20generated%20through%20a%20gain%20medium%2C%20such%20as%20a%20crystal%20or%20gas%20to%20give%20the%20molecules%20higher%20energy.%20A%20laser%2C%20which%20passing%20through%20the%20air%2C%20heats%20up%20the%20gas%20in%20its%20path%2C%20creating%20a%20turbulent%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20turbulence%20can%20cause%20the%20beam%20to%20scatter%20and%20distort%2C%20reducing%20its%20effectiveness%20and%20accuracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691995320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fp9u8jpl_laser-weapon-generic-unsplash-1200_625x300_14_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-weapons-could-soon-fire-lasers-indefinitely-after-major-breakthrough-4295993%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20military%20tested%20these%20weapons%20in%20the%20field%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20even%20destroyed%20supersonic%20missiles%2C%20they%20were%20cancelled%20owing%20to%20large%20size%20and%20weight%20of%20lasers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-weapons-could-soon-fire-lasers-indefinitely-after-major-breakthrough-4295993%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-weapons-could-soon-fire-lasers-indefinitely-after-major-breakthrough-4295993%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-weapons-could-soon-fire-lasers-indefinitely-after-major-breakthrough-4295993%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Accurately%20Do%20We%20Measure%20Poverty%20in%20India%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14120533%2F4882154176_e9f0324cee_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20decline%20in%20poverty%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20what%20a%20recent%20NITI%20Aayog%20report%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20published%20showed%20that%20over%20a%20span%20of%20five%20years%2C%20about%2013.5%20crore%20Indians%20came%20out%20of%20poverty.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20measure%20was%20of%20multidimensional%20poverty%2C%20therefore%20it%20seemed%20that%20on%20the%20whole%2C%20crores%20of%20people%20enjoyed%20the%20fruits%20of%20holistic%20progress.%20They%20are%20no%20longer%20below%20the%20poverty%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20does%20the%20methodology%20and%20its%20results%20hold%20up%20to%20closer%20examination%3F%20Has%20the%20%E2%80%98multidimensional%E2%80%99%20index%20been%20able%20to%20capture%20the%20full%20picture%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20not.%20To%20start%20with%2C%20the%20government%20of%20India%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20tell%20citizens%20the%20number%20and%20share%20of%20the%20population%20below%20the%20consumption%20poverty%20line%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20traditional%20method%20of%20estimating%20poverty%20globally%20for%20decades.%20India%20has%20used%20consumption%20poverty%20as%20the%20measure%20for%20over%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20had%20not%20released%20a%20consumption%20expenditure%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Survey%20Organisation%20(NSO)%20in%202017-18.%20The%20NSO%20has%20announced%20consumption%20expenditure%20surveys%20for%202022-23%20and%202023-24.%20These%20might%20reveal%20to%20us%20what%20has%20happened%20to%20consumption%20(or%20money-metric)%20poverty%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20has%20just%20released%20the%20national%20multidimensional%20poverty%20index%20(MPI)%20for%20India%2C%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20global%20MPI%20estimates%20were%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010%20indicators%20of%20the%20global%20MPI%20are%20a%20mishmash%20of%20very%20different%20types%20of%20indicators.%20Some%20are%20indicators%20of%20inputs%2C%20others%20of%20process%2C%20yet%20others%20are%20output%20or%20outcome%20indicators.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20education%20ones%20%E2%80%93%20having%20not%20completed%206%20years%20of%20school%20and%20children%20up%20to%20Class%208%20not%20attending%20school%20%E2%80%93%20are%20output%20and%20process%20indicators%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20ones%20are%20both%20outcome%20indicators%20%E2%80%93%20adult%20body%20mass%20index%20and%20child%20nutrition.%20All%20six%20indicators%20of%20standard%20of%20living%20are%20input-based%20%E2%80%93%20electricity%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20sanitation%2C%20cooking%20fuel%2C%20home%20floor%20and%20consumer%20assets.%20In%20statistics%2C%20it%20is%20theoretically%20flawed%20to%20lump%20together%20such%20different%20indicators%20to%20construct%20an%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENational%20and%20global%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20the%20national%20MPI%20(NMPI)%20indicator%20framework%20has%20been%20modified%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20global%20MPI%20and%20interestingly%2C%20no%20reason%20has%20been%20provided%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NMPI%20framework%20has%2012%20instead%20of%2010%20globally%20considered%20indicators.%20The%20two%20new%20indicators%20are%3A%20Maternal%20health%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98health%E2%80%99%20dimension%20and%20access%20to%20banking%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98standards%20of%20living%E2%80%99%20dimension.%20This%20addition%20leads%20to%20change%20in%20the%20weights%20assigned%20to%20the%20two%20indicators%2C%20which%20were%20the%20two%20high-contributing%20factors%20to%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20MPI%202022%20report%2C%20released%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20had%20reported%20that%20India%20had%20reduced%20its%20incidence%20of%20multidimensional%20poverty%20from%2054%25%20in%202005-06%20(National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%203)%20to%2027.9%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%20in%202015-16%20(NFHS%204)%2C%20halving%20the%20head%20count%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20that%2C%20the%20global%20MPI%20reported%20that%20the%20reduction%20in%20multidimensional%20poverty%20between%202015-16%20was%20from%2027.9%25%20to%2016%25%20in%202019-21%20(NFHS%205).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fks-james-nfhs-modi-government-data-sets-iips%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Unhappy%20With%20Data%20Sets%2C%E2%80%99%20Modi%20Govt%20Suspends%20Director%20of%20Institute%20Which%20Prepares%20NFHS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExcluding%20millions%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20global%20nutrition%20indicator%20was%20modified%20in%20NMPI%2C%20leaving%20out%20children%20aged%20six%20to%2014%20years%2C%20consisting%20of%20more%20than%2018%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population.%20More%20than%20two-third%20of%20this%20population%20group%20suffers%20from%20anemia.%20NMPI%20thus%20leaves%20many%20poor%20and%20deprived%20out%20of%20the%20count%20on%20this%20account.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%20NMPI%20uses%20undernourishment%20of%20under-fives%20(weight%20for%20age)%2C%20while%20the%20global%20MPI%20uses%20a%20more%20robust%20indicator%20%E2%80%93%20stunting%20(height%20for%20age).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20is%20higher%20(35.5%25%20in%20NFHS%205)%20in%20India%20than%20the%20underweight%20measure%20(31.1%25%20in%20NFHS%205).%20Worse%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20stunting%20rate%20is%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20Sub-saharan%20Africa%20(32%25)%3B%20just%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20child%20wasting%20rate%20is%2019.1%25%20(NFHS%205)%2C%20while%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20is%206%25%20(UNICEF%2C%202023%2C%20State%20of%20World%E2%80%99s%20Children).%20Moreover%2C%20the%20recently%20released%20%E2%80%98The%20State%20of%20Food%20Security%20and%20Nutrition%20in%20the%20World%202023%E2%80%99%20report%20by%20the%20UN%20highlighted%20that%20104.3%20crore%20(74.1%25)%20Indians%20are%20unable%20to%20afford%20healthy%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20selection%20of%20the%20new%20indicator%20on%20maternal%20health%20is%20faulty.%20It%20regards%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20to%20be%20deprived%20if%20her%20delivery%20is%20executed%20by%20an%20unskilled%20health%20personnel%20or%20if%20she%20has%20not%20availed%20the%20prescribed%20four%20antenatal%20care%20services.%20Most%20deliveries%20(more%20than%2080%25)%20are%20now%20happening%20in%20a%20health%20institution.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20there%20are%20very%20few%20deprived%20on%20this%20indicator.%20This%20will%20tend%20to%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20count%20of%20deprived%20pregnant%20women%2C%20reducing%20the%20overall%20number%20of%20persons%20falling%20under%20the%20category%20of%20multidimensionally%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirdly%2C%20take%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20addition%20of%20a%20new%20indicator%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98No%20household%20member%20has%20a%20bank%20account%20or%20a%20post%20office%20account%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20standard%20of%20living%20dimension.%20As%20per%20NFHS%204%2C%20nine%20out%20of%2010%20persons%20in%20the%20country%20(90.3%25)%20had%20either%20a%20bank%20account%20and%2For%20a%20post%20office%20account.%20While%20this%20is%20a%20major%20achievement%20for%20computation%20of%20deprivation%20and%20policy%20purposes%2C%20inclusion%20of%20this%20indicator%20significantly%20influences%20the%20overall%20number%20of%20deprived%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiffering%20data%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20and%20most%20worrying%20is%20the%20following%3A%20The%20MPI%20estimate%20for%20multidimensionally%20poor%20people%20in%20India%20in%202019-21%20estimates%20reduction%20from%20the%202015-16%20figure.%20The%20NITI%20Aayog%E2%80%99s%20report%20estimates%20the%20number%20of%20people%20rising%20out%20of%20poverty%20to%20be%20135%20million.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sleight%20of%20hand%20in%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20estimate.%20I%20double%20checked%20the%20projected%20population%20used%20for%202015-16%20and%20for%202019-21%20as%20a%20denominator%20for%20determining%20the%20absolute%20number%20of%20MPI%20poor%20in%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20exact%20population%20data%20between%20census%20years%2C%20we%20use%20population%20projections%2C%20as%20provided%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%2C%20based%20on%20Census%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20projected%20population%20in%202021%20will%20be%20higher%20than%20that%20in%202015-16.%20To%20arrive%20at%20the%20number%20of%20MPI%20poor%20for%202021%2C%20that%20year%E2%80%99s%20population%20should%20be%20used%3B%20and%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20number%20of%20MPI%20poor%20for%202015-16%2C%20again%20the%20latter%20year%E2%80%99s%20population%20should%20be%20used.%20If%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%C2%A0%20someone%20uses%20the%20same%20estimate%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20population%20for%20both%20years%2C%20the%20number%20of%20people%20pulled%20out%20of%20MPI%20poverty%20will%20be%20overstated.%20That%20is%20exactly%20what%20I%20found%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20has%20done.%20The%20estimated%20population%20for%20both%20years%20was%20found%20to%20be%20the%20same.%20The%20result%20is%20that%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20is%20claiming%20that%20India%20pulled%20135%20million%20out%20of%20MPI%20poverty%2C%20when%20in%20fact%20that%20number%20is%20really%20around%20118%20million%20(because%20the%20total%20population%20of%20India%20in%202015%20was%20naturally%20lower%20than%20in%202021).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20even%20if%20one%20goes%20by%20the%20NMPI%20estimates%20for%202019-21%20and%20projects%20it%20onto%20the%202021%20estimated%20population%2C%20410%20million%20people%20are%20still%20deprived%20on%20the%20sanitation%20indicator%20of%20NMPI.%20Yet%2C%20the%20government%20has%20claimed%20that%20India%20has%20become%20open%20defecation%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20unfortunate%20that%20government%20estimates%20fail%20to%20paint%20an%20accurate%20picture%20of%20the%20realities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESantosh%20Mehrotra%20was%20the%20chief%20economist%20of%20the%20global%20Human%20Development%20Report%20(2002-04)%2C%20UNDP%20New%20York%2C%20and%20the%20lead%20author%20of%20the%20second%20India%20Human%20Development%20Report%20(OUP%2C%202011)%20of%20the%20Planning%20Commission%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%