3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SEBI%20Seeks%2015%20More%20Days%20To%20Submit%20Report%20In%20Hindenburg%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20capital%20markets%20regulator%20SEBI%20today%20asked%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%2015%20more%20days%20to%20complete%20its%20probe%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20case%20and%20give%20a%20report.%20SEBI%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20the%20investigation%20is%20at%20an%20advanced%20stage%2C%20but%20needed%2015%20more%20days%20to%20wrap%20it%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%202%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20SEBI%20to%20investigate%20within%20two%20months%20any%20violations%20before%20and%20after%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20on%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20On%20April%2029%2C%20three%20days%20before%20SEBI's%20deadline%2C%20the%20regulator%20asked%20for%20six%20more%20months%2C%20citing%20the%20matter%20involved%20cross-border%20jurisdictions%2C%20which%20would%20take%20time%20to%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20then%20gave%20three%20months%20-%20instead%20of%20six%20-%20to%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20to%20submit%20a%20status%20report%20of%20its%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20hearing%20is%20on%20August%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20in%20the%20last%20hearing%20said%20the%20report%20by%20a%20panel%20of%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20group%20of%20domain%20experts%20to%20look%20into%20India's%20regulatory%20mechanism%20to%20protect%20investors%2C%20which%20has%20already%20submitted%20its%20report%2C%20will%20continue%20to%20assist%20the%20court%20and%20share%20the%20report%20with%20the%20parties%20involved%20in%20this%20matter%20and%20their%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20members%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20expert%20group%20who%20looked%20into%20India's%20regulatory%20mechanism%20to%20protect%20investors%20are%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20AM%20Sapre%2C%20retired%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20JP%20Devadhar%2C%20former%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20Chairman%20OP%20Bhatt%2C%20former%20ICICI%20Bank%20chief%20KV%20Kamath%2C%20Infosys%20co-founder%20Nandan%20Nilekani%20and%20securities%20and%20regulatory%20expert%20Somasekhar%20Sundaresan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20report%20given%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20May%2C%20the%20committee%20had%20said%20there%20was%20no%20price%20manipulation%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20and%20that%20the%20conglomerate%20had%20taken%20necessary%20steps%20to%20comfort%20retail%20investors.%20The%20mitigating%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20group%20had%20helped%20in%20building%20confidence%20in%20the%20stock%20and%20the%20stocks%20are%20stable%20now%2C%20the%20panel%20had%20said.%20Foreign%20portfolio%20investors%20(FPIs)%20in%20Adani%20Group%20stocks%20are%20compliant%20with%20SEBI's%20regulations%2C%20the%20committee%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20denied%20all%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20Hindenburg%20and%20called%20them%20a%20%26quot%3Bcalculated%20attack%26quot%3B%20on%20India%2C%20its%20institutions%20and%20growth%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20merely%20an%20unwarranted%20attack%20on%20any%20specific%20company%20but%20a%20calculated%20attack%20on%20India%2C%20the%20independence%2C%20integrity%20and%20quality%20of%20Indian%20institutions%2C%20and%20the%20growth%20story%20and%20ambition%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Adani%20Group%20said%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691993280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fb2d31f8o_sebi_625x300_07_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsebi-seeks-15-more-days