3.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERisque%20comedy%2C%20hope%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20creating%20a%20haven%20for%20queer%20people%20who%20can%20just%20laugh%20and%20be%20themselves%2C%20Navin%20has%20built%20a%20special%20environment.%20%E2%80%9CQueer%20people%20are%20bringing%20other%20queer%20people%20to%20my%20shows.%20My%20special%20sold%20out%20primarily%20through%20word%20of%20mouth%20because%20half%20the%20people%20at%20the%20show%20were%20queer.%20Apart%20from%20my%20solo%20shows%2C%20when%20we%20do%20the%20line-up%20shows%2C%20more%20people%20show%20up%20because%20of%20the%20diversity%20in%20the%20lineup%20and%20the%20other%20comics%20bring%20in%20their%20fanbase%20too.%20We%20have%20comics%20from%20across%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20spectrum%2C%20and%20the%20scene%20is%20developing%20for%20the%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20he%20also%20sees%20hope%20in%20the%20younger%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CUnlike%20our%20generation%20(millennials)%2C%20Gen%20Zs%20have%20their%20photo%2C%20biodata%2C%20Instagram%20link%2C%20Spotify%20link%20and%20sometimes%20even%20a%20link%20to%20their%20HIV%20test%20results%20on%20their%20social%20media%20handles.%20I%20envy%20them.%20What%20I%20love%20is%20that%20they%20have%20access.%20Growing%20up%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20YouTube%2C%20TikTok%20or%20Instagram%2C%20i.e.%20an%20outlet%20%5Bwhere%20we%20could%20express%20our%20queer%20identities%5D.%20For%20me%2C%20comedy%20was%20an%20outlet.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20them%20are%20so%20fierce%20with%20makeup.%20I%20never%20had%20the%20courage%20to%20wear%20makeup%20in%20my%20younger%20days.%20Today%2C%20you%20have%20young%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289628%2Fbengaluru-drag-artist-queen-beyonce-pride-month%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrag%