ict%E2%80%99s%20Arrah%20market%20reported%20Rs%202%2C600%20per%20quintal%20and%20even%20in%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Vadodara%20Padra%20market%2C%20prices%20touched%20Rs%202%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20this%20surge%2C%20we%20spoke%20with%20Shankar%20Darekar%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Lasalgaon%20Mandi%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20a%20region%20that%20is%20a%20major%20producer%20of%20onions.%20%E2%80%9CClimate%20change%20affected%20the%20onion%20quality%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CErratic%20rainfall%20has%20also%20affected%20other%20states%20and%20is%20responsible%20for%20late%20crops.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20about%20market%20supply%3F%20%E2%80%9CThis%20year%2C%20our%20crop%20is%20short%2C%20while%20red%20onion%20is%20still%20a%20month%20away.%20The%20Bangalore%20crop%20is%2015%20days%20late.%20April%20and%20March%20rains%20affected%20the%20crop%20in%20the%20field%20and%20in%20storage.%20There%20was%20excessive%20humidity%20and%20the%20shelf%20life%20of%20onions%20in%20godowns%20went%20down.%20Much%20of%20the%20crop%20was%20lost%20to%20fungal%20disease%2C%20which%20flourished%20due%20to%20the%20humidity%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Darekar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Ftomatoes-the-modi-government-has-made-a-pr-stunt-out-of-a-real-issue%5C%22%3E%20Tomatoes%3A%20The%20Modi%20Government%20Has%20Made%20a%20PR%20Stunt%20Out%20of%20a%20Real%20Issue%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20narrative%20brings%20us%20back%20to%20the%20failure%20of%20TOP%2C%20the%20tomato%2C%20onion%20and%20potato%20programme.%20This%20is%20the%20second%20time%20that%20State%20mechanisms%20have%20failed%20to%20control%20prices.%20NAFED%20and%20other%20agencies%20need%20to%20be%20alert%20to%20the%20imminent%20crisis%20and%20release%20buffer%20stocks%20if%20necessary%2C%20before%20onions%20reduce%20consumers%20to%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20Jawandhia%2C%20Maharashtra%20farmer%20and%20organiser%2C%20offered%20an%20alternative%20view%3A%20%E2%80%9CPrices%20are%20rising%20due%20to%20exports%2C%20which%20are%20fetching%20%24300-350%20dollars%20per%20tonne.%20Rs%2024-25%20per%20kg%20are%20the%20export%20prices.%20Malaysia%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20some%20Middle%20Eastern%20countries%20are%20the%20major%20destinations.%20Besides%2C%20some%20areas%20which%20had%20sowed%20onions%20suffered%20losses%20due%20to%20untimely%20rains%2C%20reducing%20the%20supply%20further.%20Farmers%20were%20forced%20to%20re-sow%20the%20onion%20crop%2C%20resulting%20in%20late%20harvests.%20Also%2C%20most%20of%20these%20prices%20are%20based%20on%20projections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20farmer%20gets%20Rs%202-3%2C%20no%20one%20complains%2C%20but%20when%20farmers%20start%20getting%20more%2C%20the%20government%20initiates%20measures%20to%20cut%20prices.%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20the%20government%20buy%20the%20harvest%20when%20the%20prices%20were%20at%20Rs%2013-15%20per%20kg%20and%20use%20it%20as%20buffer%20stock%3F%20That%20way%2C%20the%20farmers%2C%20the%20government%20and%20consumers%20would%20all%20be%20protected%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFood%20economy%20in%20trouble%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wheat%20export%20ban%2C%20spiralling%20prices%20of%20tomatoes%2C%20vegetables%20and%20now%20onions%20%E2%80%95%20India%20is%20displaying%20a%20series%20of%20symptoms%20of%20a%20chaotic%20food%20economy.%20Erratic%20weather%20has%20provided%20artillery%20support%2C%20pushing%20up%20prices%20of%20fresh%20produce%2C%20and%20State%20policy%20and%20price%20stabilisation%20measures%20have%20completely%20failed%20yet%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20headed%20for%20the%20moon%20but%20fails%20to%20address%20basic%20issues%20in%20the%20food%20economy%2C%20which%20can%20be%20easily%20removed%20by%20efficient%20political%20decision-making%2C%20starting%20with%20planning.%20Individual%20farmers%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20expected%20to%20track%20the%20weather%20and%20plan%2C%20but%20the%20government%20spends%20millions%20on%20space%20technology%20for%20weather%20prediction.%20They%20have%20a%20fair%20idea%20of%20what%20is%20to%20come%2C%20but%20there%20were%20no%20policy%20decisions%20for%20public%20procurement%20or%20weather%20alerts%20and%20storage%20advisories.%20Even%20if%20advisories%20were%20put%20out%2C%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20effective.%20Much%20of%20the%20onion%20crop%20was%20diseased%2C%20or%20was%20wasted%20due%20to%20low%20prices%20at%20the%20time%20of%20harvests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolicy%20planning%20on%20exports%20is%20also%20missing.%20Knee-jerk%20banning%20and%20unbanning%20of%20exports%20hurts%20both%20small%20and%20big%20traders%2C%20and%20eventually%20farmers%20and%20the%20larger%20food%20economy.%20India%20needs%20to%20have%20a%20formula%20to%20gauge%20crops%20and%20the%20export%20limits%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20the%20case%20of%20wheat%20and%20other%20agri%20commodities%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20prices%20have%20been%20volatile%20due%20to%20excessive%20exports%2C%20especially%20in%20times%20of%20scarcity.%20The%20government%20needs%20to%20wake%20up%20to%20the%20fragility%20of%20the%20food%20economy%2C%20because%20many%20see%20the%20current%20onion%20price%20inflation%20as%20strike%20three%20against%20its%20food%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%20tweets%20at%20%40Indrassingh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691988886000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14102358%2F5560910594_bdc7d1c175_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ftomato-onion-prices-inflation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Is%20this%20strike%20three%20against%20the%20Modi%20government's%20food%20policies%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ftomato-onion-prices-inflation%22%