te's%20congressional%20and%20state%20Senate%20maps%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20boundaries%20are%20unconstitutional%20and%20violate%20the%20rights%20of%20minority%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_D62515B2-AEA5-F49D-6E9B-E157319FDC08%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EThe%20suit%20alleges%20that%20the%20maps%2C%20drawn%20by%20the%20Republican-controlled%20legislature%2C%20sought%20to%20dilute%20the%20voting%20strength%20of%20Black%20citizens%20with%20lines%20around%20Memphis%20and%20Nashville%2C%20the%20state's%20biggest%20and%20most%20diverse%20population%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_D62515B2-AEA5-F49D-6E9B-E157319FDC08%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EThe%20groups%20have%20requested%20the%20US%20District%20Court%20for%20the%20Middle%20District%20of%20Tennessee%20to%20stop%20the%20%26quot%3Bcalling%2C%20holding%2C%20supervising%2C%20or%20certifying%20any%20further%20election%20in%20the%20challenged%20districts%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20current%20configurations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_D62515B2-AEA5-F49D-6E9B-E157319FDC08%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20filing%20in%20place%2C%20Tennessee%20joins%20states%20including%20Alabama%2C%20Florida%2C%20Georgia%2C%20and%20South%20Carolina%2C%20where%20lawsuits%20are%20challenging%20lines%20drawn%20after%20the%202020%20census.%20The%20resolutions%20of%20the%20cases%20could%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20which%20party%20controls%20Congress%20after%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20as%20the%20GOP%20currently%20has%20a%20slim%20222-212%20House%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_D62515B2-AEA5-F49D-6E9B-E157319FDC08%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EDebby%20Gould%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20League%20of%20Women%20Voters%20of%20Tennessee%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lawyerscommittee.org%2Fcivil-rights-groups-file-federal-lawsuit-to-block-racially-discriminatory-tennessee-redistricting%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20existing%20maps%20drown%20out%20of%20the%20voices%20of%20minority%20communities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_D62515B2-AEA5-F49D-6E9B-E157319FDC08%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20maps%20approved%20by%20the%20Tennessee%20legislature%20intentionally%20erode%20the%20voices%20of%20communities%20of%20color%20in%20Tennessee%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BTennesseans%20want%20their%20counties%20and%20their%20cities%20kept%20whole%2C%20but%20mapmakers%20ignored%20their%20interests%2C%20creating%20unfair%20districts%20that%20split%20communities%20and%20dilute%20their%20power.%20Tennessee%20district%20maps%20must%20preserve%20the%20ability%20for%20voters%20to%20express%20their%20shared%20interests%20and%20elect%20the%20political%20representation%20of%20their%20choice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_D62515B2-AEA5-F49D-6E9B-E157319FDC08%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EThe%20League%20of%20Women%20Voters%20of%20Tennessee%20is%20a%20plaintiff%20in%20the%20suit%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Tennessee%20State%20Conference%20of%20the%20NAACP%2C%20The%20Equity%20Alliance%2C%20Memphis%20A.%20Philip%20Randolph%20Institute%2C%20the%20African%20American%20Clergy%20Collective%20of%20Tennessee%2C%20and%20five%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_D62515B2-AEA5-F49D-6E9B-E157319FDC08%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20the%20creation%20of%20three%20Republican-leaning%20congressional%20districts%20that%20include%20parts%20of%20Democratic-heavy%20Davidson%20County%20but%20which%20all%20elected%20GOP%20members%20of%20Congress.%20Each%20district%20%E2%80%94%20the%205th%2C%206th%2C%20and%207th%20Congressional%20Districts%20%E2%80%94%20contains%20a%20swath%20of%20suburban%2C%20exurban%2C%20and%20rural%20communities%20which%20overpowered%20the%20vote%20in%20Davidson%20County.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_D62515B2-AEA5-F49D-6E9B-E157319FDC08%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EThe%20plaintiffs%20in%20the%20suit%20criticize%20the%20three%20aforementioned%20districts%20as%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%20racial%20gerrymanders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_D62515B2-AEA5-F49D-6E9B-E157319FDC08%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EThe%20GOP%20redistricting%20map%20eliminated%20the%20Democratic-leaning%20congressional%20district%20of%20veteran%20lawmaker%20Jim%20Cooper%2C%20who%20chose%20not%20to%20run%20for%20reelection%20in%20any%20of%20t