pan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20local%20manager%20of%20John%20Holt%2C%20a%20British%20trading%20firm%20founded%20in%20the%2019th%20century%20explained%20to%20him%20when%20Baker%20expressed%20his%20bewilderment.%20Indeed%2C%20it%20never%20had%20made%20a%20profit%20throughout%20its%20venerable%20history.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EJohn%20Holt%20was%20using%20artificially%20high%20import%20pricing%20as%20a%20mechanism%20for%20transferring%20all%20its%20profits%20out%20of%20Nigeria%20and%20back%20to%20Britain%E2%80%A6most%20foreign-owned%20companies%20were%20doing%E2%80%A6the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20Baker%20writes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECorrupt%20practice%20was%20of%20course%20inherent%20in%20colonial%20business.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChampdany%20Jute%20that%20employed%205%2C000%20Bengali%20spinners%20and%20weavers%20at%20two%20mills%20had%20only%20British%20shareholders%2C%20incorporated%20as%20it%20was%20as%20a%20Glasgow%20based%20limited%20liability%20company%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3Eyet%20even%20they%20were%20appalled%20to%20discover%20they%20had%20been%20looted%20by%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Etheir%20own%20company%20director%20Sir%20James%20Finlay%20who%20had%20paid%20Finlay%20Muir%20the%20managing%20agency%20he%20personally%20owned%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3Evast%20commissions%20(roughly%20%C2%A341%2C000%20from%201897-1900)%20even%20when%20Champdany%20had%20paid%20no%20dividends%20to%20them%20(Jones%20and%20Wales%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Business%20History%20Review%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Autumn%201998).%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBaker%20was%20soon%20to%20learn%20that%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emost%20wealthy%20Africans%20involved%20in%20foreign%20trade%20were%20illegally%20moving%20money%20abroad%20by%20the%20same%20means%2C%E2%80%9D%20employed%20by%20John%20Holt%20and%20other%20colonial%20businesses%2C%20which%20of%20course%20mirrors%20the%20very%20continuity%20that%20enabled%20Indian%20money%20laundering%20at%20the%20very%20independence%20of%20our%20country%20and%20have%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2F33-financial-fugitives-from-india-are-still-hiding-abroad-govt-data%2Farticleshow%2F88313738.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecarrying%20on%20ever%20since%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBaker%E2%80%99s%20original%20contribution%20has%20been%20to%20show%20that%20most%20%E2%80%9Cmoney%20laundering%E2%80%9D%20represents%20the%20profits%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Elegitimate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20business%20hidden%20from%20the%20fiscal%20authorities%20of%20host%20countries.%20For%20it%20is%20the%20general%20trend%20of%20international%20trade%20that%20enables%20surplus%20to%20be%20sent%20out%20of%20the%20jurisdiction%20far%20from%20the%20furious%20gaze%20of%20the%20labour%20that%20generated%20it.%20The%20prevailing%20non-cooperation%20between%20states%20enables%20a%20culture%20of%20permissiveness%20whereby%20tax%20evasion%20by%20foreigners%20in%20their%20own%20countries%20provides%20many%20western%20countries%20with%20the%20capital%20inflows%20that%20finance%20their%20trade%20deficit.%20Since%20criminal%20money%20is%20so%20easily%20hidden%20in%20the%20rush%20of%20cash%2C%20foreign%20policy%20then%20tolerates%20such%20crime%20all%20over%20the%20world%20as%20long%20as%20the%20proceeds%20land%20up%20in%20that%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBaker%20offers%20us%20a%20hypothetical%20conversation%20of%20a%20prospective%20customer%20of%20a%20US%20bank%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20make%20my%20money%20by%20smuggling%20aliens%20%E2%80%93%20men%2C%20women%2C%20and%20children%20%E2%80%93%20out%20of%20western%20China%20and%20southern%20Russia%20and%20putting%20them%20into%20the%20sex%20trade%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELooking%20%E2%80%9Cover%20the%20list%20of%20prohibited%20sources%20of%20funds%20coming%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20American%20banker%20sees%20that%20alien%20smuggling%20out%20of%20and%20into%20foreign%20countries%20is%20not%20on%20the%20list%E2%80%9D%20and%20warmly%20replies%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%20sir%3B%20we%20would%20be%20delighted%20to%20receive%20and%20manage%20your%20money.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20Baker%20shows%2C%20that%20most%20exclusive%20American%20private%20bank%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfounded%20in%201836%2C%20Riggs%2C%20catered%20to%20the%20elite%20of%20Washington%2C%20serving%2017%20presidents%20including%20Abraham%20Lincoln%2C%20generals%20and%20admirals%20including%20Sherman%20and%20Grant%20from%20the%20Civil%20War%20and%20MacArthur%20and%20Nimitz%20from%20World%20War%20II%E2%80%9D.%20Yet%20different%20standards%20applied%20when%20it%20came%20to%20dealing%20with%20Pinochet%20of%20Chile%20or%20Obiang%20of%20Equatorial%20Guinea%3B%20it%20%E2%80%9Cgrovelled%20before%20some%20of%20the%20dirtiest%20money%20on%20Earth%E2%80%A6%20KYC%20meant%20%E2%80%9CKleptocrats%2C%20You%2C%20and%20Crooks%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20this%20long-standing%20policy%20now%20threatens%20democracy%20everywhere%2C%20including%20the%20US%20itself.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20decided%20that%20the%20wealthy%20had%20more%20votes%2C%20by%20enabling%20companies%20to%20be%20treated%20as%20individuals%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20election%20finance.%20This%20enabled%20the%20seizure%20of%20power%20by%20the%20plutocracy%2C%20that%20brought%20in%20Donald%20Trump.%20The%20very%20rich%20were%20rewarded%20with%20the%20largest%20upward%20transfer%20of%20wealth%20in%20the%20shortest%20period%20in%20US%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAutocrats%20and%20oligarchs%20enable%20each%20other.%20Thus%20when%20the%20energy%20of%20the%20crowd%20was%20channelled%20into%20to%20paranoia%2C%20people%20became%20oblivious%20to%20the%20theft%20conducted%20in%20plain%20sight%2C%20as%20in%20Germany%20when%20the%20Jews%20were%20held%20responsible%20for%20every%20disaster%20while%20people%20ignored%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20enrichment%20of%20Krupp%20%26amp%3B%20Goering.%20Many%20Indians%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi1Lw53W_AkM%5C%22%3Edeceived%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20believing%20that%20%E2%80%9CSwiss%20banks%E2%80%9D%20would%20disgorge%20the%20hidden%20wealth%20of%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family%2C%20enabling%20the%20transfer%20of%20Rs%20417%20trillion%20to%20278%20million%20people.%20Today%2C%C2%A0favoured%20billionaires%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threeessays.com%2Fproduct%2Ffascism-essays-on-europe-and-india%2F%5C%22%3Egain%3C%2Fa%3E%20extraordinary%20benefits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInspired%20by%20Adam%20Smith%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETheory%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20Moral%20Sentiments%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E1759%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E)%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Baker%20maintains%20that%20corruption%20is%20no%20necessary%20feature%20of%20free%20markets%20but%20has%20subverted%20them.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20free%20markets%20have%20a%20historic%20connection%20to%20democracy.%20Peasant%20marketplaces%20enabled%20free%20trade%20without%20obligation%20to%20oppressive%20landlords%20or%20the%20Church.%20The%20Industrial%20Revolution%20needed%20free%20labour%20in%20advanced%20countries%2C%20which%20fought%20for%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20franchise%20to%20all%20adults.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20the%20value%20labour%20creates%20with%20nature%20has%20long%20been%20appropriated%2C%20degrading%20both.%20Modern%20capitalism%20was%20itself%20enabled%20by%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20expropriation%20of%20the%20European%20peasantry%2C%20genocides%20of%20Antipodean%20aborigine%2C%20Atlantic%20slave%20trade%20and%20colonial%20drain.%20Surely%2C%20reparations%20might%20be%20more%20relevant%20than%20the%20status%20quo%20ante%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20Baker%20is%20entirely%20right%20when%20he%20says%20there%20is%20now%20a%20difference%20not%20only%20of%20degree%20but%20of%20kind.%20As%20we%20have%20seen%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20authoritarians%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20no%20longer%20is%20it%20merely%20the%20rich%20from%20traditionally%20weak%20states%20who%20impoverish%20their%20own%20countries.%20Indeed%2C%20as%20the%20planet%20warms%2C%20the%20very%20rich%20do%20the%20same%20everywhere%2C%20since%20they%20are%20now%20beyond%20the%20reach%20even%20of%20powerful%20Western%20states.%20Seeking%20desperately%20to%20protect%20themselves%20from%20the%20consequences%20of%20their%20own%20actions%2C%20they%20accumulate%20more%20and%20demand%20cuts%20in%20the%20very%20taxes%20that%20pay%20for%20measures%20to%20combat%20climate%20change%2C%20hoping%20to%20insulate%20themselves%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20human%20race%20and%C2%A0%20their%20own%20folly%20%E2%80%93%20even%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20intensity%20of%20their%20extraction%20destroys%20nature%20all%20the%20more%20rapidly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClearly%20these%20multi-billionaires%20cannot%20be%20trusted%20to%20serve%20their%20own%20best%20interests%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20interests%20of%20all.%20Like%20Keynes%2C%20Baker%20would%20therefore%20like%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eeuthanise%20the%20rentier%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%2C%20in%20other%20words%2C%20to%20render%20capitalism%20which%20is%20unfettered%20at%20present%2C%20answerable%20to%20democracy%2C%20to%20save%20humanity%20and%20the%20planet%20and%20incidentally%2C%20capitalism%20from%20itself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKannan%20Srinivasan%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20writer