%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ambulance%20responded%20in%2025%20minutes.%20They%20(the%20family)%20had%20not%20sought%20an%20ambulance%20initially%20and%20took%20a%20rickshaw%2C%26quot%3B%20Brajesh%20Pathak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivpal%20Yadav%2C%20however%2C%20alleged%20that%20the%20incident%20occurred%20due%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bnon-availability%26quot%3B%20of%20an%20ambulance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state's%20health%20system%20is%20on%20ventilator%20support%20despite%20lakhs%20of%20advertisements%20and%20claims.%20A%20pregnant%20woman%20going%20to%20the%20hospital%20by%20rickshaw%20was%20forced%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20roadside%20near%20Raj%20Bhavan%20due%20to%20the%20non-availability%20of%20an%20ambulance.%20It%20is%20shameful%20for%20the%20entire%20system%20and%20it%20is%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20state's%20health%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20in%20Hindi%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691932320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F6g38s0j_lucknow-roadside-delivery_625x300_13_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnewborn-delivered-by-roadside-near-raj-bhavan-in-lucknow-dies-4294562%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20four-and-a-half-month%20pregnant%20woman%20delivered%20her%20baby%20on%20the%20roadside%20near%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20here%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20foetus%20was%20brought%20dead%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20doctors%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnewborn-delivered-by-roadside-near-raj-bhavan-in-lucknow-dies-4294562%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnewborn-delivered-by-roadside-near-raj-bhavan