0a%20professor%20somewhere%20but%20I%20realised%20I%20could%20do%20a%20lot%20better%20and%20bigger%20by%20teaching%20students.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20best%20education%20started%20after%20I%20left%20college%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20he%20started%20teaching%20in%20a%20coaching%20institute%20in%20Bengaluru.%20As%20part%20of%20his%20visits%20to%20smaller%20towns%20in%20the%20state%20for%20promotional%20programmes%2C%20he%20would%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20interact%20with%20school%20students.%20%E2%80%9CHere%2C%20I%20observed%20the%20horrible%20system%20of%20education%20we%20have.%20I%20asked%20the%20students%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20is%20a%20cloud%3F%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20is%20a%20window%3F%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20they%20looked%20up%20into%20the%20sky.%20They%20had%20no%20idea.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20education%20system%20is%20all%20about%20mugging%20things%20and%20putting%20them%20down.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F179905%2Findia-new-education-preschool-primary-curriculum-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERote%20learning%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20itself%20a%20dangerous%20thing%2C%20it%20imparts%20no%20skills%20to%20students.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20rigid%20architecture%20psychologically.%20As%20a%20teacher%2C%20your%20job%20is%20to%20manage%20a%20classroom%20of%20100%20students%2C%20it%20is%20not%20about%20teaching%20them%2C%20just%20handling%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20classrooms%2C%20the%20person%20who%20sits%20in%20the%20back%20row%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20clown.%20Others%20do%20not%20collaborate%20with%20them.%20Whenever%20a%20backbencher%20stands%20up%2C%20everyone%20bursts%20into%20laughter%2C%20that%20student%20starts%20thinking%20they%20are%20a%20%E2%80%98joker%E2%80%99%20and%20they%20lose%20the%20confidence%20to%20do%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20exp