%20and%20maintaining%20the%20sanctuary%20is%20Rs%2018%2C000%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Sai%20Vignesh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20avenues%20and%20donations%2C%20Sai%20stumbled%20upon%20an%20ancestral%20home%20that%20belonged%20to%20his%20family.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20determined%20to%20convince%20my%20parents%20to%20sell%20the%20house%20and%20help%20me%20with%20the%20funds.%20While%20it%20was%20a%20big%20decision%2C%20they%20could%20see%20that%20it%20was%20my%20only%20passion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20and%20his%20parents%20sold%20their%20ancestral%20home%20and%20purchased%20an%20eight-acre%20land%20near%20Poondi%20reservoir%20in%20Tiruvallur%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Chennai.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20help%20of%20some%20more%20donations%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20construct%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20animals.%20The%20Almighty%20Animal%20Care%20Trust%20was%20inaugurated%20in%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20cause%20started%20with%20taking%20care%20of%20stray%20dogs%2C%20his%20care%20soon%20expanded%20to%20other%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20in%20Chennai%2C%20there%20were%20sanctuaries%20for%20dogs%2C%20but%20when%20it%20came%20to%20farm%20animals%2C%20they%20had%20nowhere%20to%20go.%20Many%20bulls%2C%20buffaloes%20and%20calves%20are%20abandoned%20by%20their%20owners.%20They%20roam%20in%20the%20city%2C%20consume%20polluted%20water%20and%20food%2C%20and%20end%20up%20in%20difficult%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20dog%20gets%20hit%20by%20a%20car%2C%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20it%20will%20get%20some%20kind%20of%20help.%20However%2C%20with%20animals%20like%20sheep%2C%20cows%20and%20buffaloes%2C%20they%20are%20most%20likely%20to%20end%20up%20in%20slaughterhouses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20Sai%20to%20open%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%