akes%20so%20far%20and%20recounts%20a%20rescue%20where%20a%20child%20was%20stuck%20inside%20a%20house%20with%20a%20snake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20couple%20who%20stayed%20in%20a%20nearby%20street%20came%20running%20to%20my%20house%20one%20day.%20A%20snake%20had%20entered%20their%20house%20where%20their%20infant%20was%20playing.%20About%2050%20people%20were%20standing%20outside%20but%20no%20one%20was%20able%20to%20help%20the%20baby.%20When%20I%20entered%20the%20house%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20that%20the%20snake%20was%20busy%20trying%20to%20eat%20a%20lizard%20and%20the%20baby%20was%20happily%20playing.%20I%20caught%20the%20snake%20after%20it%20ate%20the%20lizard%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20snakes%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F193230%2Fkerala-woman-snake-rescuer-breaks-stereotypes-kochi-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20rescuer%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20also%20rescued%20and%20rehabilitated%20monkeys%2C%20black%20kites%2C%20and%20other%20birds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20the%20forest%20department%20officials%20are%20busy%2C%20they%20ask%20us%20to%20go%20for%20the%20rescues.%20I%20also%20conduct%20training%20sessions%20for%20the%20fire%20department%20officials%20along%20with%20various%20awareness%20programmes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98All%20creatures%20have%20equal%20rights%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedha4-1691583613.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vedhapriya%20has%20specialised%20in%20wildlife%20rescue%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedha4-1691583613.jpg%20