ver%2C%20was%20very%20irregular%20with%20his%20work%20because%20of%20his%20addictions.%20He%20would%20go%20one%20day%20and%20stay%20home%20for%20the%20next%20five.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20add%20to%20these%20woes%2C%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20understand%20the%20local%20dialect%2C%20and%20thus%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F278803%2Fias-hero-uplifts-jharkhand-sabar-tribes-from-poverty%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efind%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20herself.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20just%20desperate%20to%20bring%20food%20into%20the%20house.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20see%20my%20children%20starving%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonths%20of%20misery%20were%20followed%20by%20a%20ray%20of%20hope%20when%2C%20one%20day%2C%20Rekha%20went%20knocking%20on%20homes%20for%20food.%20While%20at%20it%2C%20she%20learnt%20that%20a%20carpet%20business%20was%20training%20women%20in%20the%20fine%20art%20of%20carpet%20weaving%20and%20paying%20them%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20going%20off%20to%20work%20was%20unheard%20of%20in%20the%20village%20at%20that%20time%2C%20shares%20Rekha%2C%20adding%20that%20her%20decision%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277365%2Fwicker-story-priyanka-narula-ratan-cane-craftsmen-hyderabad-furniture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoin%20the%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20met%20with%20resistance%20both%20in%20and%20outside%20her%20home.%20%E2%80%9CI%20fought%20it%20and%20went%20anyway%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20proudly%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Rekha%20is%20among%20the%201%2C800%20women%20trained%20by%20Obeetee%20%E2%80%94%20a%20legacy%20Indian%20brand%20that%20prides%20itself%20on%20its%20handmade%20carpets%20and%20rugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERekha%E2%80%99s%20journey%20with%20Obeetee%20grew%20with%20the%20passing%20years.%20And%20today%2C%20this%