anxiety.%20It%20was%20overwhelming%20and%20stressful%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20were%20so%20many%20things%20wrong%20with%20my%20brain%20and%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20medicate.%20The%20stigma%20and%20lack%20of%20support%20and%20empathy%20drove%20me%20to%20find%20the%20help%20and%20guidance%20I%20needed.%20The%20excel%20sheet%20with%20people%E2%80%99s%20real%20life%20experiences%20gave%20me%20the%20confidence%20to%20book%20an%20appointment%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Maneka%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20first%20interaction%20helped%20me%20immensely%20because%20my%20emotions%20and%20fears%20were%20heard%20and%20not%20invalidated.%20The%20first%20few%20sessions%20helped%20me%20see%20life%20in%20a%20different%20light%20and%20the%20advice%20and%20guidance%20she%20provided%20regarding%20how%20to%20handle%20my%20professional%20and%20personal%20life%20has%20helped%20me%20turn%20my%20life%20around.%20I%20have%20now%20been%20off%20my%20medication%20and%20am%20capable%20of%20dealing%20with%20life%20confidently%20due%20to%20the%20help%20and%20guidance%20provided%20by%20Rohini%20and%20The%20Able%20Mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormally%20launched%20in%20April%202022%2C%20The%20Able%20Mind%20is%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316087%2Fassam-couple-helps-rural-northeast-india-access-affordable-mental-healthcare-mita%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emental%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20venture%20that%20has%20created%20an%20online%20and%20offline%20platform%20to%20allow%20anyone%20to%20connect%20with%20a%20certified%20psychotherapist%20for%20Rs%20500%20a%20month.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20was%20founded%20by%20Rohini%20Rajeev%2C%20a%20social%20worker%2C%20psychotherapist%20and%20a%20licensed%20marital%20therapist%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20Rajeev%20Vijayan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20empathy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Tiruchirappalli%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F293356%2Fhealth-benefits-of-kanji-fermented-rice-water-ancient-south-india-food-science%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Rohini%20completed%20her%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20medical%20and%20psychiatric%20social%20work%20from%20a%20local%20college%20in%202002.%20Today%2C%20she%20is%20a%20doctoral%20scholar%20enrolled%20with%20the%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Sciences%20(TISS)%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20obtaining%20a%20PhD%20in%20Social%20Sciences%20with%20just%20a%20semester%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20course%20in%20social%20work%20gave%20me%20the%20opportunity%20to%20participate%20in%20intensive%20training%20provided%20by%20a%20variety%20of%20social%20impact%2C%20non-governmental%20and%20government-run%20hospitals%20and%20psychiatric%20wards%2C%20etc.%20To%20prove%20ourselves%20valuable%20to%20society%2C%20we%20were%20taught%20to%20overcome%20our%20own%20stereotypes%20and%20biases%20before%20even%20thinking%20of%20supporting%20another%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rohini.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClinical%20social%20work%20and%20psychiatry%20is%20a%20difficult%20and%20incredibly%20heartbreaking%20line%20of%20work%2C%20but%20it%20gave%20me%20an%20opportunity%20to%20help%20clients%2C%20particularly%20those%20who%20found%20little%20or%20no%20acceptance%20anywhere%20else.%20I%20began%20in%20residential%20rehabilitation%20(for%20people%20experiencing%20a%20dependence%20on%20alcohol%20or%20other%20drugs)%20and%20continued%20to%20gain%20knowledge%20on%20the%20job%20while%20also%20receiving%20training%20to%20support%20people%20experiencing%20different%20types%20of%20emotional%20distress%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%2022%20years%2C%20Rohini%20has%20transitioned%20from%20actively%20working%20in%20rehabilitation%20to%20practising%20psychotherapy%20with%20individuals%2C%20couples%2C%20and%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_323802448_1220338928909950_7840996380178594020_n_1080-1691411771.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rohini%20Rajeev%20is%20making%20mental%20health%20therapy%20affordable%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_323802448_1220338928909950_7840996380178594020_n_1080-1691411771.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_323802448_1220338928909950_7840996380178594020_n_1080-1691411771-300x215.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_323802448_1220338928909950_7840996380178594020_n_1080-1691411771-500x358.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_323802448_1220338928909950_7840996380178594020_n_1080-1691411771-768x550.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FSnapinsta.app_323802448_1220338928909950_7840996380178594020_n_1080-1691411771-150x107.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326558%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22773%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERohini%20Rajeev%2C%20founder%20of%20The%20Able%20Mind%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccessible%2C%20affordable%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20The%20Able%20Mind%2C%20Rohini%20ran%20a%20small%20private%20practice%20established%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20it%20was%20heartening%20to%20be%20able%20to%20support%20those%20who%20reached%20out%20to%20me%20for%20help%20via%20other%20clients%20or%20referred%20by%20psychiatrists%20and%20general%20physicians%2C%20it%20was%20just%20before%20the%20pandemic%20when%20my%20husband%20and%20the%20co-founder%20Rajeev%20Vijayan%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98technology%20whizz%E2%80%99%2C%20came%20up%20with%20an%20idea.%20He%20began%20building%20an%20online%20platform%20for%20people%20to%20reach%20out%20more%20easily%20and%20also%20make%20consultations%20simpler%20and%20the%20counselling%20practice%20more%20scalable%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Rohini.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEase%20of%20accessibility%20and%20the%20affordability%20of%20the%20consultations%20helped%20me%20expand%20my%20counselling%20practice%20and%20the%20user%20base%20increased%20especially%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20This%20encouraged%20other%20private%20practitioners%20to%20join%20my%20platform%20as%20affiliate%20consultants%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20on%20from%20this%2C%20between%20December%202021%20and%20February%202022%2C%20Rohini%20and%20Dr%20Jessy%20Fenn%2C%20a%20faculty%20member%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Psychology%2C%20Rajagiri%20College%20of%20Social%20Sciences%20in%20Kochi%2C%20carried%20out%20a%20pan-India%20survey%20on%20the%20state%20of%20mental%20health%20amongst%20youngsters%20above%20the%20age%20of%2016.%20The%20study%20focussed%20on%20young%20people%E2%80%99s%20attitude%2C%20approach%20and%20acceptance%20of%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20results%20of%20the%20unpublished%20study%20threw%20light%20on%20the%20mental%20health%20challenges%20our%20youngsters%20endure%20including%20anxiety%2C%20depression%2C%20body%20image%20issues%2C%20relationship%20challenges%20and%20loneliness%2C%20etc.%20The%20study%20also%20endorsed%20the%20fact%20that%20three-fourth%20of%20the%20respondents%20experienced%20emotional%20distress%20and%20mental%20health%20concerns%20over%20a%20six-month%20period%20but%20almost%20the%20same%20percentage%20of%20them%20did%20not%20seek%20professional%20mental%20health%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rohini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20their%20study%2C%20these%20respondents%20did%20not%20seek%20help%20due%20to%20the%20fear%20of%20being%20judged%2C%20lack%20of%20awareness%20and%20time%2C%20extreme%20stigma%2C%20inadequate%20access%20to%20professional%20help%20especially%20in%20smaller%20towns%20and%20high%20cost%20of%20therapy.%20In%20fact%2C%20according%20to%20a%202023%20study%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1050928%2Fhigh-mental-healthcare-costs-are-pushing-indian-families-into-poverty%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMental%2520health%2520expenditure%26amp%3Btext%3DAccording%2520to%2520National%2520Sample%2520Survey%2CRs%252041%252C239%2520for%2520private%2520hospitals.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJournal%20of%20Health%20Management%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20if%20a%20member%20of%20a%20household%20is%20suffering%20from%20a%20mental%20health%20illness%20they%20spend%20on%20average%20Rs%202%2C115%20each%20month.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20all%20those%20inputs%20into%20consideration%2C%20Rohini%20and%20Rajeev%20developed%20a%20mental%20health%20support%20app%20with%20some%20key%20features.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FThe-Able-Mind-Team-Image-1691411231.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bengaluru%20startup%20engages%20in%20proactive%20mental%20health%20therapy%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FThe-Able-Mind-Team-Image-1691411231.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FThe-Able-Mind-Team-Image-1691411231-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FThe-Able-Mind-Team-Image-1691411231-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FThe-Able-Mind-Team-Image-1691411231-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FThe-Able-Mind-Team-Image-1691411231-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326544%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Able%20Mind%20team%20working%20towards%20proactive%20and%20preventive%20mental%20health%20support%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20day%2C%20everyday%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Able%20Mind%20app%20powers%20our%20text%20based%20services%20that%20allow%20clients%20to%20seek%20brief%20counselling%20services%20through%20live%2015%20minute%20chat%20sessions%20with%20a%20counsellor%20or%20asynchronous%20text-based%20psychotherapy%20(therapy%20over%20text).%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7291694%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20shown%20that%20text-based%20therapy%20has%20been%20as%20effective%20as%20regular%20therapy%20in%20case%20of%20mild%20and%20moderate%20mental%20health%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Rajalakshmi%20R%2C%20a%20certified%20clinical%20hypnotherapist%20and%20trauma%20informed%20counsellor%20with%20a%20decade%20of%20clinical%20experience%20who%20works%20with%20The%20Able%20Mind%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%2015-minute%20chat%20gives%20users%20the%20opportunity%20to%20access%20help%20when%20they%20are%20going%20through%20a%20difficult%20time%20without%20waiting%20for%20an%20appointment%20or%20having%20to%20go%20through%20a%20long%20process%20of%20screening.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20additionally%20offer%20counsellor-led%20peer%20group%20sessions%20over%20chat%20and%20audio%2C%20a%20forum%20to%20collaborate%20and%20share%20personal%20stories%20anonymously%2C%20self%20help%20tools%2C%20assessments%2C%20a%20free%20resource%20hub%2C%20affirmative%20messages%20that%20empowers%20people%20to%20take%20care%20of%20their%20mental%20health%20proactively%20one%20day%20at%20a%20time%2C%20on%20our%20app%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rohini.%20They%20also%20conduct%20workshops%2C%20mental%20health%20awareness%20sessions%2C%20POSH%20(prevention%20of%20sexual%20harassment)%20consulting%20services%20and%20curated%20%E2%80%98wellbeing%20training%20programs%E2%80%99%20for%20corporates%20and%20individuals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20teenager%20is%20looking%20for%20help%2C%20all%20our%20support%20options%20(online%20and%20offline)%20are%20available%2C%20but%20they%20need%20to%20be%20registered%20by%20a%20parent%2Fguardian.%20It%20is%20mandatory%20for%20parental%20consent%20to%20be%20sought%20for%20those%20under%2018%20in%20India%20before%20psychological%20support%20is%20provided.%20Once%20registered%2C%20the%20details%20of%20the%20session%20will%20be%20kept%20completely%20confidential%20unless%20we%20are%20dealing%20with%20psychosis%2C%20neurosis%20or%20self-harm%20given%20the%20legal%20mandate%20we%20operate%20under%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Rohini.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20sets%20The%20Able%20Mind%20apart%20from%20other%20such%20mental%20healthcare%20service%20providers%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Rohini%2C%20%E2%80%9CUsers%20have%20direct%20access%20to%20a%20psychotherapist%20via%20an%20app%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20book%20an%20appointment.%20We%20offer%20preventive%20mental%20health%20services%20to%20help%20people%20avoid%20everyday%20stressors%20from%20building%20up.%20This%20reduces%20the%20risk%20of%20developing%20severe%20mental%20health%20issues%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20We%20also%20provide%20continued%20support%20that%20mitigates%20worsening%20of%20mental%20health%20symptoms%3B%20thus%20taking%20care%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20mental%20health%20remains%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20hands.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20further%2C%20she%20points%20out%20that%20their%20services%20are%20affordable%20at%20Rs%20500%20a%20month%2C%20and%20they%20offer%20text-based%20therapy%20and%20support%20in%20nine%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246205%2F83-yo-kerala-school-dropout-creates-unique-dictionary-in-4-south-indian-languages-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregional%20languages%3C%2Fa%3E%20apart%20from%20English.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20employ%20bots.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20we%20use%20technology%20to%20support%20therapy%3B%20not%20to%20provide%20it.%20Also%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20look%20at%20mental%20health%20purely%20from%20the%20lens%20of%20counselling%20but%20we%20also%20aim%20to%20empower%20individuals%20with%20the%20right%20support%20and%20tools%20(meditation%2C%20breathwork%2C%20music)%20and%20techniques%20to%20take%20control%20of%20their%20own%20mental%20health%20wherever%20they%20might%20be%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Able%20Mind%20has%20a%20team%20of%20about%2020%20in-house%20experienced%20mental%20health%20professionals%20with%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20psychology%20and%20at%20least%20250%20hours%20of%20supervised%20counselling%20experience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20example%20of%20Nikkita%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20consultant%20psychologist%20from%20Darjeeling%2C%20who%20has%20in%20the%20past%20worked%20with%20neurodivergent%20children%20employing%20play%20and%20art%20therapy.%20She%20is%20also%20a%20certified%20trauma%20counsellor%20and%20an%20expert%20in%20adult%20ADHD%20(attention-deficit%2