ne%20person%E2%80%99s%20trash%20is%20another%20person%E2%80%99s%20treasure.%E2%80%9D%20Carrying%20the%20sentiment%20forward%2C%20Gayatri%20started%20to%20look%20for%20ways%20of%20using%20the%20mammoth%20amount%20of%20bottles%20in%20her%20storage%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20she%20found%20%E2%80%98Kavi%20The%20Poetry-Art%20Project%E2%80%99%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286048%2Fbest-home-decor-influencers-interior-design-diy-recycle-ideas-tips-on-instagram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20venture%20that%20converts%20glass%20waste%20into%20pieces%20of%20home%20decor%20and%20utensils.%20Founded%20by%20Noida-based%20Madhuri%20Balodi%20and%20Amit%20Singh%2C%20the%20project%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F314356%2Fkerala-woman-upcycles-waste-glass-into-home-decor-vapasee-sustainable-venture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollects%20glass%20bottles%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20ragpickers%20and%20customers%2C%20and%20converts%20them%20into%20serving%20sets%2C%20platters%2C%20drinking%20glasses%2C%20lamps%20and%20other%20such%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20never%20seen%20anyone%20do%20this%20before%2C%20so%20I%20spoke%20to%20them%2C%20I%20resonated%20with%20their%20ideology%20so%20much%20that%20I%20shipped%20six%20cartons%20full%20of%20bottles%20to%20them.%20They%20made%20me%20all%20sorts%20of%20things%20like%20planters%2C%20platters%2C%20vases%2C%20wine%20glasses%2C%20jars%20and%20lamps%20from%20these%20bottles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20quality%20of%20the%20products%20is%20so%20good%2C%20I%20have%20gifted%20so%20many%20of%20those%20pieces%20to%20my%20friends%20and%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gayatri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETesting%20